NK103(pe)020:1: // shes rab kyi spyan rnam par 'byed pa'i man ngag bzhugs /
NK103(pe)020:2: ma rig pa'i rab rib kyis shes rab kyi spyan
NK103(pe)020:3: mdongs pa la tshig gi thur mas rnam par 'byed
NK103(pe)020:4: pa zhes bya ba'i tshegs chung la don chen po
NK103(pe)020:5: 'grub pas man ngag /'khrul pa mnyam pa'i klong du
NK103(pe)020:6: bcom sangs rgyas kyi yon tan ma lus par ldan
NK103(pe)020:7: mu matha'i phyogs ris las 'das gsang sngags sku lnga'i
NK103(pe)020:8: sdud pa mdzad cing rang gi nye 'khor la 'chad
NK103(pe)020:9: pas gsang ba'i bdag po 'gro ba'i don mdzad pas
NK103(pe)020:10: dpal las kyi gnod sbyin 'dul bas phyag g.yas pa
NK103(pe)020:11: na rdo rje bsnams pa de la phyag 'tshal lo
NK103(pe)020:12: // sangs rgyas chos dang 'phags pa'i dge 'dun gyi tshogs dang /
NK103(pe)020:13: rang gi dngos 1kyi dang rgyal ba rig 'dzin gang zag brgyud pa'i bla 111ma dang //
NK103(pe)020:14: las kyis 'brel ba'i yi dam gyi lha dang bka'
NK103(pe)020:15: srung ma mo rnam pa gsum la sogs bstan srung
NK103(pe)020:16: dang // bdag gi phyag gis mchod par 'os shing
NK103(pe)020:17: rigs pa kun la'ang thun mong dang khyad par gyi
NK103(pe)020:19: se'i ban+de bdag gis dngos dang brgyud pa'i gdul byar gyur pa yi //
NK103(pe)020:20: rgyud dang man ngag gi gzhung rgyas pa'i tshig gis
NK103(pe)020:21: 'jigs te slob par mi nus pa'i gang zag rnams
NK103(pe)020:22: la // snying brtse ba'i bsam pa sems kyis kun bslangs nas //
NK103(pe)020:23: rgyas pa ma yin par mdo tsam zhig rjod kyis khang du chub par gyis shig ces gdams pa /
NK103(pe)020:24: thams cad rang rjod bya snang du ye nas lhun
NK103(pe)020:25: gyis grub kyang ma rtogs shing phyin ci log tu
NK103(pe)020:26: brtags pas bsgribs nas mi gsal ba de rjod byed
NK103(pe)020:27: ston byed gzhung rnam par bkod pa 'di nyid kyi
NK103(pe)020:28: ngag gis brjod bya'i don dgos pa rtogs pa'i ngang
NK103(pe)020:30: sgrib byed rang sar grol te sku gsum yang dgos
NK103(pe)020:31: du lhun gyis grub pa ni thabs byung gi tshul
NK103(pe)020:32: du 'brela pa te dgos 'brel dang ldan bas //
NK103(pe)020:33: chos kyi rjes su 'brang ba'i rtog ldan 'jug pa'i yul du gyur pa'i man ngag 'di //
NK103(pe)020:34: mdo sde dang rgyud sde dang bstan bcos man ngag
NK103(pe)020:35: 0dag las btus pa'i tshig las gzhan na med pa
NK103(pe)020:36: de dag gi mtshams sbyor ba tsam zhig rtog ge
NK103(pe)020:38: de 0yis de 0la mi gnod pa'i phyir yang mtshams sbyar te de la rten pa yin pa'i phyir //
NK103(pe)020:39: tshad ma'i ston pa sangs rgyas kyi gsung bzhin du gus pas blang bar rigs pa yin no //
NK103(pe)020:40: rtsom pa po 'jug pa'i bya ba de dag gi
NK103(pe)020:41: rjes su lus yan lag rgyas pa la khyab pas
NK103(pe)020:43: slob dpon sh+r+ai sid+ha'i rin po che phreng ba las /
NK103(pe)020:44: dang po rang gi shes rab kyi rgyud thos pas bkrol nas //
NK103(pe)020:45: rtogs goms rig pa'i rtsal sbyang ste de'i bar du gcod pa'i bdud brtag cing //
NK103(pe)020:47: blo sbram gyi rgyud dgrol ba'i phyir snang bzhi'i don gtan la dbab pa dang /
NK103(pe)020:48: rig pa'i rtsal sbyang ba'i phyir man ngag gi yan
NK103(pe)020:49: lag slob dpon slob ma man ngag gsum bstan pa'o
NK103(pe)020:50: // dang po ni ye shes gsang ba'i rgyud las /
NK103(pe)020:51: ma bcos pa rang bzhin rang rig pa ma 'gags
NK103(pe)020:52: par snang ba ni ye nas gzhir gnas pa yin
NK103(pe)020:53: // zug rngu med pas bde bar mngon du mdzad
NK103(pe)020:54: pas gshegs pa gdul bya'i ngo la sna tshogs su
NK103(pe)020:55: snang ba ni nyes pa gnyis zad pas 'bras bu
NK103(pe)020:56: // yin // gzhung bshad pa'i go rim gdul bya
NK103(pe)020:57: 'khor gyi blo dang 'tshams par bstan pa snang ba
NK103(pe)020:58: byang chub kyi sems su blo 'jug pas lam pa
NK103(pe)020:60: thams cad 'byung bas gzhi rang bzhin gyi snang ba dang //
NK103(pe)020:61: mngon par rtogs pa'i go rim shes thob kyi byed
NK103(pe)020:62: pa gnyis dang ldan pas lam gdul bya'i snang ba
NK103(pe)020:63: dang // mthar phyin bskyed du byar med pas 'bras bu bde bar gshegs pa'i snang ba'o //
NK103(pe)020:64: gsum po de dag thams cad du bdag gcig /
NK103(pe)020:68: 'thob byed du 'brel cing thams cad tshang ba'i phyir rgyud rngam klog las /
NK103(pe)020:69: 'brel dang ma tshang med pa dang //
NK103(pe)020:70: phun sum tshogs pas rgyud ces bya //
NK103(pe)020:71: zhes gsum du yang gsungs te /
NK103(pe)020:72: sangs rgyas gsang ba'i thugs kyi thigs pa las /
NK103(pe)020:75: 1 / snang 111ba gsum gyi ngo bo ka la //
NK103(pe)020:76: gzhi lam 'bras bu rgyud gsum kyi dbye ba rnam par gzhag /
NK103(pe)020:78: de dag ngo bo nyid gcig pa la tha dad gsum du snang ba ni gang gis phye na /
NK103(pe)020:80: gcig la snang ba gsum gyi ngo bor snang ba yang //
NK103(pe)020:81: de ma yin la der 'dzin pas 'khrul pa'i las
NK103(pe)020:82: mi mthun pa sna tshogs su snang bas phye bas
NK103(pe)020:84: des na snang ba bzhi dag 1tu /
NK103(pe)020:85: gang las na lung 3rigs kun 0las ji ltar na gsal bar 2bshad /
NK103(pe)020:87: ji ltar phye na rin po che rgyan las kyang /
NK103(pe)020:88: ma nor bar rang bzhin gyis snang ba ni bsgribs pas 'khrul snang shar //
NK103(pe)020:89: lam brgyud pa'i gdams pas sgrib byed dang bral bar
NK103(pe)020:90: mngon du byas te mthar phyin cing brtan pa ni
NK103(pe)020:91: 'bras bur snang ba'i ldog cha tha dad las snang
NK103(pe)020:92: ba gsum du bgrangs kyang don gyis ngo bo gcig
NK103(pe)020:94: 'khrul pa'i snang bas 0phye bar gsungs pa'i phyir /
NK103(pe)020:95: de nyid 0gzhi'i zhor la bshad pas snang ba bzhir 0'gyur ro //
NK103(pe)020:96: de 0la rang bzhin gyi snang ba ni //
NK103(pe)020:97: rin po che rgyan las ye nas gnas pa rang bzhin gyi snang ba'i ngo bo mtshon pa'i dpe //
NK103(pe)020:98: ming don nges pa'i tshig ming gi rnam grangs brdar btags pa'i dgos ched dang //
NK103(pe)020:99: yin lugs kyi rang bzhin mtshon pa'i mtshan nyid gnas pa'i dus //
NK103(pe)020:102: brgyad po de la dang po ngo bo ni /
NK103(pe)020:103: rgyu rkyen med pa'i rang 0rig pa ci'i 0ngo bor yang ma grub pa nyid //
NK103(pe)020:104: ji ltar 0bltas pa bzhin 'khor 'das sam snod bcud thams cad du rang snang yang /
NK103(pe)020:105: rang 1rig pa kho na las gzhan pa med pa ste /
NK103(pe)020:106: de skad du la shan las /
NK103(pe)020:107: rgyu rkyen med pas rang 0byung thams cad du rang
NK103(pe)020:108: snang ba nyid byang rang bzhin chub rnam pa sems
NK103(pe)020:109: mtshan nyid // spros 0pa thams cad dang bral ba
NK103(pe)020:110: ni rang rgyud pa shes pa lnga'i yul min na'ang
NK103(pe)020:111: mtshan nyid // // grub pa med pa nyid ngo
NK103(pe)020:112: bo nyid kyi rgyu btags 0so cog tu chags gang
NK103(pe)020:113: ltar bsgrubs par 'grub pa de nyid //
NK103(pe)020:114: rig pa rang snang ba yin pa'i phyir phyi snod dang nang bcud kyi dngos po kun tu //
NK103(pe)020:115: rang snang mtshan nyid ma 'dres par so so snang ba rnams gcig par ston pas yang zhes bya'o //
NK103(pe)020:116: sems 1nyid yin pa'i phyir rang bzhin gyi rtags rtog pa med cing ma bsgribs pas 'od gsal ba'i //
NK103(pe)020:117: sems nyid las sel med pas 'ba' zhig kho na bas //
NK103(pe)020:118: mu mtha' cir yang snang ba la phyogs gcig pa gang du yang gzung du med pa'o //
NK103(pe)020:120: gnyis pa dpe ni dper na gser kasa le sbram
NK103(pe)020:121: la bzo'i rnam pas tha khadad kyang ngo bo gagser
NK103(pe)020:124: d+ho bzhu ba'i rgyu karkyen dang mgar ba'i las kyis ma byas pa'i //
NK103(pe)020:125: gser sa le sbram gyi gong bu las byas pa'i rdzas shol zangs rgyan sku rnams kun //
NK103(pe)020:130: tha dad bzhi po ngo gabo gser du gcig pa ltar te mthun dape'o //
NK103(pe)020:132: spyir ni rang snang dag gi yon tan gyi phyogs
NK103(pe)020:133: re nam mkha' rgya mtsho la sogs pa kun gyis
NK103(pe)020:135: don ji lta bar dpe gang gis kyang mtshon du med par gter gtad las /
NK103(pe)020:136: kun nas mtshon pa'i dper las 'das //
NK103(pe)020:137: dmus long mar gyi mdog mtshon 'dra //
NK103(pe)020:140: gsum pa nges tshig ni rang bzhin zhes pa la
NK103(pe)020:141: ni chos gsum tshang dgos te de yang ngo bo
NK103(pe)020:142: rgyu rkyen gyis ma bskyed pa yin te rang bzhin
NK103(pe)020:144: 'byung bar rigs pa ma yin no //
NK103(pe)020:146: rgyal po in+d+ra b+hu ti'i lam rnam bkod las /
NK103(pe)020:147: rgyu dang rkyen dang byed pa pos byas pa min par //
NK103(pe)020:148: rang bzhin gyi ngang nyid kyi snang tshul gyis //
NK103(pe)020:150: rang bzhin gzhan du mi 'gyur ba yin te /
NK103(pe)020:152: rang bzhin gzhan du 'gyur ba ni //
NK103(pe)020:153: nam yang 'thad pa ma yin no //
NK103(pe)020:156: 'gre log dang spyi'u tshugs te 'khor 'das gar song yang //
NK103(pe)020:157: snying po'i gshis kyi yin lugs kyi don las 'da' ba rang mi srid pa yin //
NK103(pe)020:159: rnam 'jog chos gzhan la mi ltos pa yin te rtsa she las /
NK103(pe)020:160: rang bzhin dag ni bcos min dang //
NK103(pe)020:161: gzhan la ltos pa med pa yin //
NK103(pe)020:163: nam mkha' che las nam mkha' bzhin du rang bzhin mtha' mnyam zhing bltos sa ltos chos med //
NK103(pe)020:164: gzhan la bltos par gyur na ni rang bzhin gyi chos ma yin //
NK103(pe)020:167: ye shes gsang ba'i rnam pa ma 'gags pa ni //
NK103(pe)020:168: 'khor 'das sna tshogs su snang bas snang ba zhes de la ci la yang ngos gzung med //
NK103(pe)020:170: rim gsum las 'khor 'das kyi tha snyad gnyis kyi chos rnams kun //
NK103(pe)020:171: ma lus pa 'byung ba'i phyir na gzhi zhes bya //
NK103(pe)020:172: zhes pa ni gzhi'i ming don no //
NK103(pe)020:173: bzhi pa ming grangs ni gdul bya'i zhen pa dgrol ba'i phyir ming du mar btags te /
NK103(pe)020:175: rgyan las gdul bya'i blo yi 'tsham tshang du btags pa ni //
NK103(pe)020:176: spros pa rang gsal bas byang sems 1rtsol ba med
NK103(pe)020:177: pas lhun grub 1zug rngu med pas bde chen 1dang
NK103(pe)020:178: // yul med pas rang snang mtha' dang bral bas dbu ma bzang ngan med pas mnyam pa nyid //
NK103(pe)020:179: lhag ma med pas rdzogs pa chen po rgyur gyur pas chos kyi dbyings //
NK103(pe)020:180: tha dad ma grub pas gnyis med blo las 'das
NK103(pe)020:181: pas bsam 'das byed pa po med pas ma bcos
NK103(pe)020:183: ming grangs la mtha' med pas rgyal bas kyang rjod pa las 'das //
NK103(pe)020:185: brjod du med pas tha snyad du btags pa ci'i yang don min pa ste //
NK103(pe)020:186: ming gi rnam grangs ni gdul bya'i zhen pa dgrol ba'i ched du btags par zad //
NK103(pe)020:187: ces kyang la shan las gsungs so //
NK103(pe)020:188: lnga pa de ltar dgos ched kyi dbang gis ming
NK103(pe)020:189: du mar btags kyang rang snang gi dgos ched rnam
NK103(pe)020:190: pa sgyu ma dang mthun pas gud na med do
NK103(pe)020:191: // 'dir khyad par lhun grub gsum du btags pa ni /
NK103(pe)020:192: rgyan las dgos ched gnyis phyir brdar btags te mtha' gsum bsal kate rtogs pa don du khagnyer //
NK103(pe)020:193: ther kazug rtag par 'dzin pa dang rol pa'i snang ba chad par lta ba dang /
NK103(pe)020:194: rtag chad gnyis dang bral ba la bltos pa'i dbus 'dzin pa'i //
NK103(pe)020:195: mtha' de gsum bsal phyir rang bzhin /
NK103(pe)020:197: mtshan nyid du brdar gdags 0kyi sgra ji bzhin du zhen pa ni min no //
NK103(pe)020:198: shes khabya tshogs brgyad nyon yid nga bdag las gzung 'dzin dang //
NK103(pe)020:199: yid spros pa sna tshogs dang /
NK103(pe)020:200: sgo lnga yul la mtshan ma lngar 'dzin pa dang
NK103(pe)020:201: gsal ba skye lugs gsum po rang sku gsum du
NK103(pe)020:202: grol bar bstan pa'i phyir yang lhun grub gsum du
NK103(pe)020:204: zhes 'byung bas sgra ji bzhin par ni don mi gzung ngo //
NK103(pe)020:205: drug pa rang bzhin ni mtshan nyid 'dzin pa'i chos 'khor 'das thams cad kyi chos nyid yin te /
NK103(pe)020:206: ye shes gsang ba'i rang bzhin ni //
NK103(pe)020:207: sangs rgyas sems can gnyis su med //
NK103(pe)020:208: nam mkha' yis lus can kun la khyab pa bzhin du kun la khyab //
NK103(pe)020:211: ye shes gsang ba las gzhi don lhun grub rnam gsum la //
NK103(pe)020:212: rnam pa 1sgyu ma rang bzhin 1spros bral mtshan nyid
NK103(pe)020:213: 1rang rig rnams lhun gnas kyi bde 111ba chen por
NK103(pe)020:217: da ltar dus gsum gyi bde bar gshegs pa'i ye shes dang //
NK103(pe)020:218: 'gro ba rigs drug gi sems kyi ma bcos pa //
NK103(pe)020:219: tha dad pa ma yin te rang bzhin gcig /
NK103(pe)020:221: bdun pa mtshan nyid phyogs gcig par gzung du med de /
NK103(pe)020:222: rim gsum las mtshan nyid ni phyogs gcig pa'i mtha' rnams kun dang bral bas //
NK103(pe)020:223: phyogs cir yang blos gzung du med pa'o //
NK103(pe)020:226: de yang ngo bo dang mtshan nyid ril lhun gyis grub pa'i bdag nyid /
NK103(pe)020:227: mu bzhi mtha' drug kun dang bral bas thig le nyag gcig mu mtha' ji yang ma spangs pa /
NK103(pe)020:228: phyogs med kyang phyogs kun kyi dngos gzhi /
NK103(pe)020:229: ris can du snang yang ris dang bral ba ni //
NK103(pe)020:230: sgron ma sangs rgyas nyid kyis kyang 'di ltar yin zhes brtag par mi zin pa ni //
NK103(pe)020:231: yod par sgro 'dogs med par skur pa 'debs pa
NK103(pe)020:232: dang ngang gis bral bas na skabs las nges pa'i
NK103(pe)020:233: mkha' khyab byang sems kyi lung zhes kyang bsnyad do
NK103(pe)020:234: zhes gsungs so // brgyad pa dus ni rang byung
NK103(pe)020:235: gi ye shes rgyu rkyen gyis ma bskyed pas dus
NK103(pe)020:236: gsum du mi 'gyur ba mi rtag pa kun gyi
NK103(pe)020:237: ngo bo nyid kyi yin kyang phyogs gcig tu mi
NK103(pe)020:239: rgyan rgyu yis bskyed pa la mi gnas par rang snang yin bas //
NK103(pe)020:240: thog ma med cing mthar mi nub //
NK103(pe)020:242: gnyis pa 'khrul pa'i snang ba ni /
NK103(pe)020:244: 'khrul gzhi dngos po'i gnas lugs 'khrul tshul blo'i snang
NK103(pe)020:245: ba dang 'khrul kyang chos nyid las mi 'gyur ba'i
NK103(pe)020:247: sdom des 'khrul snang nges par shes par bya //
NK103(pe)020:249: dang po 'khrul gzhi ni mu bzhi mtha' drug mnyam pa nyid du grol 0ba nyid yin te /
NK103(pe)020:251: lta klong las de 0ye nas gnas pas na mnyam grol de la gzhi byas pas //
NK103(pe)020:252: de ngo ma shes ngar 'dzin pa las 'khrul pa'i rtog pa sna tshogs su shar //
NK103(pe)020:254: mu matha'i phyogs gcig pa yin na mu mtha' thams cad du 'char du mi rung ste /
NK103(pe)020:256: lta klong mnyam grol de min yod med gnyis gnyis
NK103(pe)020:257: med kyi mu bzhi skye 'gag rtag chad 'gro 'ong
NK103(pe)020:258: gcig tha dad kyi mtha' brgyad 'khor 'das chos //
NK103(pe)020:259: cir yang 'char bar mi rigs pa la 'char ba de yi phyir //
NK103(pe)020:260: chos can 'khor 'das thams cad kyi chos nyid du
NK103(pe)020:261: gnas lugs de rigs so 'os so gasha'o 'thad do
NK103(pe)020:263: dgongs 'dus yin lugs ci yang med par snang tshul cir yang rig pa nyid do //
NK103(pe)020:265: gnyis pa 'khrul tshul ni spyan 'grel las /
NK103(pe)020:267: tshul dang nyes pa 'grub pa'i byed pa po dang //
NK103(pe)020:268: nye bar mtshon pa'i dpe dang brgyad kyis rnam par dbye //
NK103(pe)020:270: rgyu ni bshad pa bzhin du rang bzhin gyi snang
NK103(pe)020:271: ba yin kyang de nyid kyi phyir yul du ma
NK103(pe)020:272: grub cing / rtogs pa'i rkyen lhun gnas rgyu la bshes gnyen bdag /
NK103(pe)020:273: sems skye rim pas go phye ste //
NK103(pe)020:274: rdzogs lung dmigs pas don rig pa //
NK103(pe)020:276: bzhi dang bral bas nges par ma byas pa 1ni
NK103(pe)020:277: lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pa zhes bya ste
NK103(pe)020:278: / thog ma 'byung snga bas gnas lugs dang mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu'o //
NK103(pe)020:279: rgyu 1des sbyor don la bdag tu bzung zhing bdag
NK103(pe)020:280: gzhan tha dad du snang ba 0ni kun tu brtags
NK103(pe)020:281: pa'i ma rig pa zhes bya ste lhan cig byed
NK103(pe)020:282: pa'i rgyu'o // rkyen ni des 0nyon mongs pa dug
NK103(pe)020:283: lnga rgyas nas zhe sdang gis dmyal ba ser snas
NK103(pe)020:284: pa'i rgyu'o // yi dwags / gti mug gis dud 'gro /
NK103(pe)020:286: phrag dog gis lha ma yin /
NK103(pe)020:287: nga rgyal gyis lhar skye ba'i rkyen byed pa la sogs pa dang /
NK103(pe)020:288: nyon mongs pa de dag gis kun nas bslangs nas
NK103(pe)020:289: ngan 'gro'i lus dang longs spyod yid du mi 'ong
NK103(pe)020:290: ba ni bsod nams ma yin pa ste 'bras ming
NK103(pe)020:291: rgyu la btags pa'i las mi dge ba bcu rnams
NK103(pe)020:292: che 0'bring 0chung 0bar spyad pas ngan song dmyal 0yi
NK103(pe)020:293: 0dud 0gsum du rim pa ltar skye zhing /
NK103(pe)020:294: yid du 'ong ba bsod nams kyi 3lus 4ngag /
NK103(pe)020:295: 3yid kyi las dge bcu byings che 1chung 2gis 'dod
NK103(pe)020:296: khams kyi lha 1drug dang mir 2bzhi 'phen par byed
NK103(pe)020:297: de rdzogs byed ni dge sdig gang gis rdzogs nges
NK103(pe)020:299: rnam smin gzhan du mi g.yo ba'i las zag pa dang bcas pa'i tshad med byams /
NK103(pe)020:304: dpyod pa dga' bde btang snyoms kyis bzhis gzugs khams kyi ltar zhing /
NK103(pe)020:307: yod min med min gyi snyoms 'jug bzhis gzugs med
NK103(pe)020:308: kyi lha bzhir skye ba'i rkyen byed par mdo rgyud
NK103(pe)020:310: 'bras bu ni rgyu rkyen de dag gi dbang gis
NK103(pe)020:311: snod bcud bsam gyis mi khyab par snang ba ste
NK103(pe)020:312: / de skad du rtsa rgyud las /
NK103(pe)020:313: sna 1111tshogs pa'i lus 1bzang ngan dang longs 1spyod che chung dang //
NK103(pe)020:314: gnas 1mtho dman dang sdug 1basngala las nyon mongs la sogs pa //
NK103(pe)020:315: bshad pa de dag la bdag dang bdag gir so sor 'dzin /
NK103(pe)020:316: ces gsungs pa de dag la bden par grub pa
NK103(pe)020:317: ni rdul dang skad cig tsam yang med par la
NK103(pe)020:318: shan las / dngos kun log rtog tsam nyid las /
NK103(pe)020:319: phra dang skad tsam yod ma yin //
NK103(pe)020:320: 'khrul pa'i snang ba zhes su gsungs //
NK103(pe)020:323: dus ni ya mtshams rgyas pa las /
NK103(pe)020:324: thog ma med nas sems yan btang /
NK103(pe)020:325: 'di nas 'khrul med cing dus gsum yang dag sgron ma las /
NK103(pe)020:326: dus gsum thad rang ma 'khrul na //
NK103(pe)020:330: dal klong rgyan tshad las 'das pas tha ma'ang bral rgyun du 'khor /
NK103(pe)020:331: mi zad par rgyun du mi stongs par 'byung bas thog mtha' med par gsungs la /
NK103(pe)020:332: rgyu rkyen gyis bskyed cing skad cig ma'i skye 'gag dang bcas pa dang /
NK103(pe)020:333: rgyud bla'i 'grel par mdo khungs drangs pa /
NK103(pe)020:334: thog med gyur kyang tha ma dang ldan pa //
NK103(pe)020:336: bdag med kyi lam nyams su blangs pa rnams grol
NK103(pe)020:337: bas spyan 'grel las bltos pa'i glo bur ba yang
NK103(pe)020:339: du rdzogs pa 'khor ba'i shes pa glo bur ba /
NK103(pe)020:340: rang bzhin ma yin rkyen gyis snang //
NK103(pe)020:343: bram skor 'khor 'das gnyis la thog mtha' yod //
NK103(pe)020:345: thog mtha' yod par gsungs par go'o //
NK103(pe)020:346: 'khor ba'i tshul ni gter gtad las gsum gyi rlung drag po mthu che bas //
NK103(pe)020:347: zhen pa 'gro ba drug gi 'khor lo las kyi shugs kyis yang nas yang du bskyar //
NK103(pe)020:349: ris drug tu 'khor tshul mthar chags sam yan man ma nges par 'khor zhing /
NK103(pe)020:350: rten 'brel bcu gnyis kyis 'khor tshul ni /
NK103(pe)020:351: thugs thigs las phyi dang nang gi rten 'brel gyi 'khor los rigs drug gi gnas su bskyor ba'ang //
NK103(pe)020:352: khams gsum gyi cha yis grangs bcu gnyis kho nar nges pa med //
NK103(pe)020:355: rgyan las sdug bsngal gsum dang brgyad la sogs pa'i sna tshogs pa'i nyes pas rang gi rgyud nyen //
NK103(pe)020:356: gnas skabs thar pa dang mthar thug bde ba chen po'i srog dang bral ba'o //
NK103(pe)020:358: byed pa po ni rgyu rkyen med pa'i sems nyid
NK103(pe)020:359: thams cad du rang snang ba ni ma bcos pa'i
NK103(pe)020:360: skad cig ma ste 'khor 'das thams cad ngo bo
NK103(pe)020:363: kun byed las byang chub sems kyis kun byas gcig kyang ma byas //
NK103(pe)020:364: kun byas te byang chub nyid kyi rang bzhin byas //
NK103(pe)020:365: gcig kyang ma byas pa de kho na nyid la bya mi dgos //
NK103(pe)020:367: rgyun gyi skad cig ma rig 0ma rig 0gnyis kyis 'khor 0'das 0gnyis su snang ba las /
NK103(pe)020:368: 'dir ma rig pa rgyun gyi skad cig ma ste /
NK103(pe)020:369: rim gsum rgyun dang bcas pa'i skad cig ma ni /
NK103(pe)020:370: las kyi 'khor ba'i byed pa por brjod pa'o //
NK103(pe)020:372: dpe ni dus rgyun du 'khor ba ni rgyan las /
NK103(pe)020:373: rgyun du mi stong 'khor lo bskor zo chu brgyud pa'i 'khor lo ltar zhes so //
NK103(pe)020:375: du mar mched pa ni rgyas pa las r+ts+wa sog me dpe 'khor lo bzhin /
NK103(pe)020:376: long btags rgyas shing brgyud par 'gyur /
NK103(pe)020:378: gi me mched pa dang 'dra zhing /
NK103(pe)020:379: med bzhin phyi rol don du snang ba ni dbang po rgyan las /
NK103(pe)020:380: yod pa ma yin don ltar snang /
NK103(pe)020:381: rkyen gyis dkrugs pa'i dbang po bzhin /
NK103(pe)020:383: bslad pas skra zla la sogs pa snang ba bzhin te /
NK103(pe)020:384: chos nyid rang snang yang gzhan phyin ci log du
NK103(pe)020:385: 'dzin pa ni lta klong las thag pa la sbrul
NK103(pe)020:387: srin bu'i kha chu la sogs pa bzhin no //
NK103(pe)020:388: gsum pa rang bzhin ni chos brgyad po de ltar
NK103(pe)020:389: du 'khrul pa sna tshogs kyis rgyud bslad kyang sems
NK103(pe)020:390: nyid pas rang bzhin gyi snang ba las 'gyur zhing
NK103(pe)020:394: rang bzhin nyid las nyams pa med //
NK103(pe)020:395: de lta bu yin na'ang dper na /
NK103(pe)020:396: rgyal po phru gu dmangs su 'khyams kyang rgyal po'i
NK103(pe)020:397: sha khrag rigs las mi 'gyur ba de bzhin du
NK103(pe)020:398: rang bzhin chos nyid kyi rigs las 'gyur ba med
NK103(pe)020:399: pas / shul lam gyis bsgrubs pa'i don 'bras bu rang las 'byung gi gzhan las min phyir //
NK103(pe)020:400: rgyas pa las ngan song gsum rgyud 'gro ba rigs
NK103(pe)020:401: drug sna tshogs pa gcig nas gcig tu rgyu ba
NK103(pe)020:402: yang // 'khrul pa'i log pa'i rtog pa blo nyid snang ba ste //
NK103(pe)020:403: de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings la 'khrul pa 'gyur ba med //
NK103(pe)020:406: rigs pa gnyis kyis phye nas bstan pa gdul bya'i blo dang 'tsham par snang ba ste /
NK103(pe)020:407: thugs thigs las rang bzhin 1las 2kyis 10phye ba yi //
NK103(pe)020:409: blo dang mos pa'i snod tha dad pa dang bcud
NK103(pe)020:410: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa dang sbyar ba'i theg pa
NK103(pe)020:411: bsam yas pa'ang / gdul bya'i snang ba zhes su ngag tu brjod //
NK103(pe)020:413: de'i don rtogs shing nges par bya ba ni /
NK103(pe)020:415: ji ltar cang shes gyi ling dag /
NK103(pe)020:416: sdom byed sgrog gis bcings gyur pa //
NK103(pe)020:417: bkrol byas bde blag btang gyur na //
NK103(pe)020:418: ci la'ang thogs med 'gro ba ltar //
NK103(pe)020:419: sems kyi cang shes dbang po 'di //
NK103(pe)020:420: mi shes bcings bas bcing gyur pa //
NK103(pe)020:421: dam pas rnam grol sgo phye nas //
NK103(pe)020:422: shes rgyud kun grol thogs med 'gro //
NK103(pe)020:424: phreng ba las rang rang gi 'dod pa shan dbye
NK103(pe)020:425: spang du med par la bzlas pas blo sbram gyi
NK103(pe)020:426: rgyud khrol la // snyan khung brgyud pa'i gdams pas chos nyid mngon sum du stan cig /
NK103(pe)020:428: rang rang gi grub pa'i matha'i skyon /
NK103(pe)020:429: gtan la phab ste shan dbye ba dang /
NK103(pe)020:430: mu bzhir bsdus te byang chub kyi sems su la bzla ba ste rdzogs chen rang gzhung bstan pa'o //
NK103(pe)020:432: dgongs 'dus kye grogs po dag theg pa'i sgo shan dbye bar bya ba ni 'di lta ste /
NK103(pe)020:433: gzhi chos nyid ji bzhin pa yi de kho na //
NK103(pe)020:434: nyid du nges pa'i ngo bo las lta ba tha
NK103(pe)020:435: dad 'byung ba ni gang zhe na rig 1pa dang
NK103(pe)020:437: chos kun 1gyi chos nyid shes nas spyod pa 'das
NK103(pe)020:438: pa dang las 'bras dang de kho na nyid la
NK103(pe)020:439: kun 0tu rmongs pa 'jig rten pa'i lta ba rnam
NK103(pe)020:440: pa gnyis su snang ba las /
NK103(pe)020:441: nang ris su dbye na tha dad du ma mang por 'gyur //
NK103(pe)020:443: 'jig rten pa dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i theg pa gnyis te //
NK103(pe)020:444: dang po'ang las rgyu 'bras la yod med du rtog
NK103(pe)020:445: dpyod zhugs pa grub mthas blo bsgyur ma zhugs pa
NK103(pe)020:446: ma bsgyur gyis gnyis su 'gyur te /
NK103(pe)020:448: las 'bras la rmongs pa'i lta ba rnam pa gnyis
NK103(pe)020:449: su snang ba las rgyu 'bras la ma dpyad pas
NK103(pe)020:450: mi shes pa dang dpyod kyang mthar lhungs pas log
NK103(pe)020:451: par shes pa'o // mi shes pa la phyal pa
NK103(pe)020:452: ni chos thams cad la rgyu 'bras yod med du
NK103(pe)020:453: par shes pa'o // ma rtogs pa'o // rgyang 'phen
NK103(pe)020:454: zhes bya ste tshe 'di'i ched du phan pas sam
NK103(pe)020:455: par shes pa'o // ma rtogs pa'o // / pa
NK103(pe)020:456: ni tshe snga phyi ma rtogs shing gsang tshig la
NK103(pe)020:457: brten nas tshe 'di'i btsan phyug dang mthu stobs sgrub
NK103(pe)020:458: par shes pa'o // ma rtogs pa'o // / pa'o // gnyis zhes gsungs la //
NK103(pe)020:459: log par rtog pa la yang /
NK103(pe)020:460: mu stegs rang bzhin gyis log dmus long dang 'dra
NK103(pe)020:461: gzhan gyi rkyen phral du long ba 'dra log pa
NK103(pe)020:462: de ka la nang pa'i theg pa dgu'i zhar las
NK103(pe)020:464: ces pa'i bye brag la yang /
NK103(pe)020:465: spyan ras gzigs brtul zhugs nas /
NK103(pe)020:466: brgya nyi shu la dus gsum gyi chas phye bas lta log sum brgya drug cu rtsa gnyis /
NK103(pe)020:471: de bzhin du phung po bzhi la'ang sbyar /
NK103(pe)020:472: log pa'i ri bo nyi shu /
NK103(pe)020:473: 'jig tshogs su lta ba la sogs pa mthar 'dzin /
NK103(pe)020:475: lta ba la tshul khrims dang brtul zhugs mchog tu 'dzin pa dang /
NK103(pe)020:477: sngon gyi mtha' la rtog pa thams cad rtag par rtog pa bzhi /
NK103(pe)020:478: kha cig rtag par rtog pa bzhi /
NK103(pe)020:479: rgyu med smra ba rnam pa gnyis /
NK103(pe)020:480: mtha' la rtog pa bzhi dang ni /
NK103(pe)020:481: lha mi spong bar rtog pa bzhi /
NK103(pe)020:482: bco brgyad 'di dag sngon gyi mtha'/
NK103(pe)020:484: phyi ma'i mtha' la rtog pa zhe 'du shes can rtog bcu drug dang /
NK103(pe)020:485: 'du shes med par rtog pa brgyad /
NK103(pe)020:486: 'du shes yod min med min brgyad /
NK103(pe)020:487: chad par lta bdun mthar lta lnga /
NK103(pe)020:488: bzhi bcu rtsa bzhi phyi ma'i mtha'/
NK103(pe)020:489: drug cu rtsa gnyis bden par lta /
NK103(pe)020:493: phyogs ltos gcod pa gang zhe na /
NK103(pe)020:494: phyi rol bye tha rang phra zab rgya rig 11byed /
NK103(pe)020:501: de re re la'ang gsum gsum ste nang tshan bcu
NK103(pe)020:502: gnyis la sogs pa bye brag brjod kyis mi lang
NK103(pe)020:503: ba yang rtag chad gnyis su 'dus te /
NK103(pe)020:505: shes pa rang bzhin gyis log pa dang gzhan rkyen
NK103(pe)020:506: gyis cha mthun par gol ba'i rtsa ba gnyis las
NK103(pe)020:507: / gong du bstan pa'i bye brag du ma'ang gnyis su 'dus te /
NK103(pe)020:511: log par rtog pas mtha' zad cing pha rol tu
NK103(pe)020:512: mi phyin pas mur thug mya ngan las 'das pa'i
NK103(pe)020:513: rgya mtshor 'bab pa'i lam gyi chu rgyun gyi mu
NK103(pe)020:514: la rten 'cha' ba skad du zer bas /
NK103(pe)020:518: don lhag rtog ge ba mur thug chad lta la
NK103(pe)020:519: rigs gsum las tshe snga phyi dang las rgyu 'bras
NK103(pe)020:520: // mi 'dod par tshe 'di tsam stes dbang las glo bur du byung bar 'dod pa dang /
NK103(pe)020:521: 'gro ba yang mi dang dud 'gro las gzhan mi 'dod /
NK103(pe)020:522: la la snga phyi tsam 'dod la sems can rnams
NK103(pe)020:523: nyon mongs pa dug gsum gyi rang bzhin yin pas
NK103(pe)020:525: thar pa mya ngan las 'das pa 'thad pa min
NK103(pe)020:526: te dug gsum dang sems gnyis yod na mnyam chad
NK103(pe)020:527: na chad mnyam du 'dod pa dang rgyal ba'i lung
NK103(pe)020:529: bral ba mnyam par gsungs la /
NK103(pe)020:530: bral ba'i phyogs kyi ngang tshul zur tsam bzung nas
NK103(pe)020:531: khas len thams cad spangs te ma yin pa'ang ma
NK103(pe)020:533: 'di dag gi 'dod pa dbral dka' yang dag pa'i don la gzud pa dka' bas /
NK103(pe)020:534: nang pa la mos pa'i las can thabs 'dzud bsre
NK103(pe)020:535: phyogs su lhung ba rnams logs lta'i nyes dmigs kyi
NK103(pe)020:536: nyen gyis bstang / blo spyi sar 'jog pa la
NK103(pe)020:537: rtog ge tshad ma gsum gyis sun dbyung ste thabs
NK103(pe)020:538: du mas nang par gzud pa dpa' bos gter gtad
NK103(pe)020:539: nyen gyis bstang / du gsungs / zhes 'byung ba la //
NK103(pe)020:540: spyod pa'i dka' thub ni med la /
NK103(pe)020:541: rdo rje'i rgyud 'byung ba gang las gyur pa'i lus de zhig pas //
NK103(pe)020:542: lus dang sems 'byung ba bzhi'i bag la zha ste gnas //
NK103(pe)020:543: dus tshe phyin chad phan gnod kyi chos la dgos pa med pa'i phyir //
NK103(pe)020:544: lus sems gdung ba'i dka' thub kyi 'bad rtsol mi dgos so //
NK103(pe)020:547: kho rang gi zhe 'dod dang mi mthun par ngan song kho nar 'gro bar 'bras klong /
NK103(pe)020:549: ngang tshul mi brtan lhung ba'i gnas /
NK103(pe)020:552: don lhag log pa'i shes pa rtag pa'i dngos por smra ba ni rig pa 1rdul 1phra rab kyi /
NK103(pe)020:553: yon tan gsum gyi rang bzhin 1 /
NK103(pe)020:554: dbang phyug 1rnams rtags 1111pa gcig pu bde ba rang dbang thob pa /
NK103(pe)020:555: rgyu de dag las byung ba dang byed pa po
NK103(pe)020:556: de dag gis byas pa'i 'bras bu rnams 'gyur bas
NK103(pe)020:557: mi rtag cing mi gtsang ba'i dri mas gos 0par
NK103(pe)020:559: de dag rgyu dang 'bras bu la log par yang lta ste /
NK103(pe)020:560: lta rim de yang rgyu med rgyur smra ba //
NK103(pe)020:561: rang bzhin rgyur 'dod dbang phyug rgyu //
NK103(pe)020:562: ngo bo nyid la rgyur smra dang //
NK103(pe)020:563: rdul phran rgyu ru 'dod pa dang //
NK103(pe)020:564: byed po rgyu ru 'dod pas log /
NK103(pe)020:568: rgyur lta ba de dag khrus dang gtsang sbra la
NK103(pe)020:569: spyad pas bdag rtag pa de dag pa thob par
NK103(pe)020:570: lta // yang na 'tsho ba gtsang bar bcos pa
NK103(pe)020:571: nang par srung ba ste sangs rgyas pa las dag
NK103(pe)020:573: dus kyi rgyun la lhwam gyi cha lugs dang gos kyi kha dog bcos pa dang //
NK103(pe)020:574: skra dang kha spu bregs pa'am ral par bcos dang lus thal ba'am thod pa'i rgyan cha dang //
NK103(pe)020:575: dbyug gu gsum pa la sogs dbyar gyi zhes drang pa /
NK103(pe)020:578: de 0dag par bya ba'i phyir rang gi tshul snga
NK103(pe)020:579: ma las bsgyur ba'i khyi dang bya'i brtul zhugs ngal
NK103(pe)020:580: la 'bras bu med pas log chos spyod //
NK103(pe)020:583: log par lta ba'i gcer bu pa ni dbang phyug
NK103(pe)020:584: chen po gdugs dkar po bzung ba'i dbyibs 'dra ba'i
NK103(pe)020:585: lus // tshangs pa dang khyab 'jug gnyis ni lha chen po'i lus po //
NK103(pe)020:586: bye brag pa rdul phra rab las grub pa'i snying
NK103(pe)020:587: gi dkyil gyi bdag de dri ma dang bral ba'i
NK103(pe)020:588: lus // grangs can pa spyi rnam 'gyur gtso bo
NK103(pe)020:589: la thim pas gzugs bdag ya bkar du gnas pas
NK103(pe)020:591: rig byed pa rig pa'i dngos po rtag pa gcig pu bde ba //
NK103(pe)020:592: rang dbang can du gnas pa shel lta bu dag pa'i lus su 'dod //
NK103(pe)020:593: de dag kyang gzugs khams kyi ris kyi lha yi bye brag 'ga' zhig dang //
NK103(pe)020:594: dngos su gzugs med skye mched ris bzhi la gnas pa yin //
NK103(pe)020:595: 'das par 'dod kyang bdag tu 'dzin pa yod pas 'jig rten pa dngos yin no //
NK103(pe)020:598: don lhag lha chen tshangs pa dang khyab 'jug la
NK103(pe)020:599: sogs pa gang zag dam pa ma yin pa'i lung
NK103(pe)020:600: la rang gi bsam gtan gyi nyams kyis sgrub ste
NK103(pe)020:601: // zag pa nyon mongs pa dang bcas pa'i mngon
NK103(pe)020:602: shes phra mos rnal 'byor gyi mngon sum dang mi
NK103(pe)020:603: dmigs pa'i rtags kyi nges par bcad kyang mi 'thad
NK103(pe)020:604: // de // khyed 'dod pa'i rtag pa'i dngos po des bdag dang gzhan gyi don sgrub pa la //
NK103(pe)020:605: rim dang cig car du brtags na mi 'thad 'khrul par shes pa yin no //
NK103(pe)020:607: 'jig rten pa de dag dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i khyad par ni /
NK103(pe)020:608: lha rje bde gshegs mkhas pa dag gis rtsa ba
NK103(pe)020:609: lta ba rtag chad kyi mthar lhung ma lhung gcig
NK103(pe)020:610: yan lag gsum 'jig rten gyi lha la skyabs su
NK103(pe)020:611: 'gro mi 'gro / dkon mchog la dad mi dad /
NK103(pe)020:613: sgrub byed khams gsum las 'da' mi 'da' 'bras bu
NK103(pe)020:614: khyad par du gyur par gsal sgron du gsungs la
NK103(pe)020:615: / nya ri pa mdor na grub mtha' 'dzin tshul gyi khyad par ni /
NK103(pe)020:617: ji ltar gang zag gi bdag tu 'dzin pa de ltar kun nas nyon mongs pa 'khor bar bstan /
NK103(pe)020:618: sems la bdag dang yul la bdag gir mi dmigs
NK103(pe)020:619: rnam par byang ba mya ngan las 'das par gsungs
NK103(pe)020:621: rten gyi gang zag gi khyad par ni /
NK103(pe)020:623: rang dbang med par skye rga na 'chi'i duhkha bzhi ldan pas 'jig rten pa zhes bya /
NK103(pe)020:627: rga 1ba'i sdug 111basngala rtsa ba nas spangs //
NK103(pe)020:628: las dang nyon mongs yod pa'i dbang gis skye ba'i sdug bsngal 'byung yang /
NK103(pe)020:629: 'phags pa de la las dang nyon mongs pa de med pa'i phyir skye ba de med //
NK103(pe)020:630: ces pa ni khyad par ro //
NK103(pe)020:631: 'das pa'i theg pa de la'ang grangs kyi rkyen rnam grangs pa gnyis te /
NK103(pe)020:632: rang spyi'i mtshan ming nyid ma 'dres par kyi bstan
NK103(pe)020:633: pa'i theg pa ni lam 'bras bu dang bcas pa'o
NK103(pe)020:634: // rang bzhin rdo rje'i theg pa'o //
NK103(pe)020:635: dang po la mtshan nyid gtsor ston par 'dra yang
NK103(pe)020:636: skal ba mos pa dbang po'i bye brag gis gsum
NK103(pe)020:637: ste / 'bras bu thob kar yang bshes gnyen la
NK103(pe)020:638: nyan cing thos par byed thos pa'i 'bras bu gzhan
NK103(pe)020:639: la sgrogs pas thos sgrogs zhes kyi theg pa dang
NK103(pe)020:640: ste / / rang don du 'bras bu sangs rgyas kyi bsgrub pa'i theg pa dang //
NK103(pe)020:641: 'bras bu byang chub ni gzhan don du thob par
NK103(pe)020:642: bya ba'i phyir sems dpa' ba'am bstan pa'i theg pa'o
NK103(pe)020:645: lta sgom spyod 'bras gtan tshigs mdo /
NK103(pe)020:646: zhes pas lta ba dang sgom pa dang spyod pa dang 'bras bu de dag sun dbyung ngo //
NK103(pe)020:648: rdul phra rab 1dang skad cig ma la phyogs 1dang dus kyi 1cha shas med pa ni /
NK103(pe)020:649: gzhig gzhom gyis mi gnod pas don dam pa'i bden par grub la /
NK103(pe)020:654: chos tsam gzung ba'i yul 1'dzin pa'i sems rdul 1phran
NK103(pe)020:655: dang skad cig mar ni gzhig gzhom gyis mi gnod
NK103(pe)020:656: pas don dam pa'i bden par grub la /
NK103(pe)020:657: blos gzhig cing gnyen pos gzhom du rung bas rags
NK103(pe)020:658: pa dang rgyun de ni kun rdzob kyi bden pa
NK103(pe)020:660: bye brag tu smra ba'i bshad mdzod chen mo'i rjes su 'brang ba dang /
NK103(pe)020:661: theg pa chung ngu'i mdo sde'i rjes su 'brang ba'i mdo sde pa'i lta ba mi mthun pa ni /
NK103(pe)020:662: dbang po dang don du phrad pa'i blo yul drug
NK103(pe)020:663: gi rnam pa bzhag pa med kyang thug phrad la
NK103(pe)020:664: gzung 'dzin dus mnyam du skye ba ste gzhan rig
NK103(pe)020:666: yul gyis bzhag pa'i rnam pa dang bcas par shes
NK103(pe)020:667: pa skye ste snga phyi'i gzung 'dzin 'dod cing rang
NK103(pe)020:668: myong ba dang gzhan dmigs pas 'dzin pa'i bye brag
NK103(pe)020:669: dang / gong bu'i mtshan nyid la yang rdul phra rab rnams skor ba bar dang bcas pa ste /
NK103(pe)020:670: rlung gi mthus bsdus par 'dod pa dang /
NK103(pe)020:671: bar med la 'byar ba yang ma yin pa po ti bsdams pa ltar 'dod pa dang /
NK103(pe)020:672: gzhan yang 'das ma 'ongs dang dbyibs dang rig byed
NK103(pe)020:673: ma yin pa'i gzugs rdul phran gyi rdzas su dang
NK103(pe)020:674: 'dus ma byas / gsum po rnams rtag pa'i rdzas dang med dgag dang /
NK103(pe)020:675: mi ldan pa'i 'du byed rnams gzugs /
NK103(pe)020:676: sems sems byung gsum las gzhan pa'i rdzas gsum gyi
NK103(pe)020:677: gnas skabs rdzas su bye brag pa 'dod pa dang
NK103(pe)020:678: mdo sde pa mi 'dod pa'i bye brag kyang yod
NK103(pe)020:680: bye brag tu smra ba nyid la yang /
NK103(pe)020:681: gang zag rdzas su ni yod /
NK103(pe)020:682: phung po dang gcig gam tha dad rtag mi rtag
NK103(pe)020:683: brjod du med par 'dod pa dang de ltar mi
NK103(pe)020:684: 'dod pa dang / rten bcas kyi mig gis gzugs rnams mthong rten bcas /
NK103(pe)020:685: de la brten pa'i rnam shes min //
NK103(pe)020:686: gang phyir bar du chod pa yi //
NK103(pe)020:687: gzugs ni mthong ba min phyir lo //
NK103(pe)020:688: bar 'dod pa dang mi 'dod pa dang /
NK103(pe)020:689: kha che dang yul dbus kyi bye brag tu smra
NK103(pe)020:690: ba rnams kyang lta ba phra mo mi mthun no
NK103(pe)020:691: zhes 'byung ngo // sgom pa ni blo gros rab 'dus byas thams cad mi rtag /
NK103(pe)020:692: skye ba thams cad sdug bsngal /
NK103(pe)020:694: mya ngan las 'das pa zhi bar bsgom 'bring rnam
NK103(pe)020:695: rtog gi gnyen por rlung tha ma 'dod chags kyi
NK103(pe)020:696: gnyen por mi gtsang ba gsum gyi sgom tshul rnams
NK103(pe)020:697: las dang po ba yir gsal te sgom klong nas
NK103(pe)020:699: spyir ni lta phreng las 'phags pas rtogs shing kha
NK103(pe)020:700: cig rang bzhin yin pas pa'i phyin ci ma log
NK103(pe)020:701: pas bden pa bzhi sgom pa'i rim gyis //
NK103(pe)020:704: ji ltar sgom na rgyud bla ma las /
NK103(pe)020:705: nad ni ngo shes par bya ba la nad kyi
NK103(pe)020:706: rgyu ni sman dang dpyad kyis spang bar bya la
NK103(pe)020:707: / nad dang bral ba'i bde bar gnas pa de
NK103(pe)020:708: thob par bya ba'i phyir sman ni bsten par bya
NK103(pe)020:709: / ba ltar / sdug bsngal 0gyi bden pa dang /
NK103(pe)020:711: de dang bral ba 'gog pa dang /
NK103(pe)020:712: de bzhin du 'thob par byed pa'i lam0 /
NK103(pe)020:717: zhes 'byung ba bzhin du sgom te /
NK103(pe)020:718: de dag re re la bzhi bzhi rnam pa bcu
NK103(pe)020:719: drug dang ldan par chos bzod pa dang rjes su
NK103(pe)020:720: bzod pa dang / chos shes pa dang rjes su
NK103(pe)020:721: shes pa'i ye shes bden pa re re la sbyar
NK103(pe)020:722: bas bcu drug gis rtogs par bya'o //
NK103(pe)020:725: dge ba dang mi dge ba'i chos thams cad kun
NK103(pe)020:726: rdzob shes pa la snang ba dang don dam ye
NK103(pe)020:727: shes la'ang snang pa gnyi gar so sor yod par
NK103(pe)020:728: phan tshun 'gal bas bden par min kyang lta bas
NK103(pe)020:729: / lus ngag gi dge ba ni spyod sdig pa
NK103(pe)020:730: ni spong ba ni tha pa sa'i sgras gdungs pa'i
NK103(pe)020:731: don ni dka' thub ste 'bras bu 'dod pa'i phyir
NK103(pe)020:732: lus gdung bar byed pa dang b+ha dwa'i sgras bsgyur
NK103(pe)020:733: ba'i don ni brtul zhugs te 'bras bu'i yon tan
NK103(pe)020:734: 'dod pas rang gi tshul snga ma las sgyur ba'i
NK103(pe)020:738: dge ba bcu dang sdig pa bcu'i las la yang rtsa ba bzhi gtso bor bstan cing //
NK103(pe)020:739: sems can gzhan la gnod par 'gyur ba'i sbyor ba rnam pa kun tu spangs nas //
NK103(pe)020:740: rgyu nyes spyod tha dad spangs pas 'bras bu rnam
NK103(pe)020:741: smin so sor las thar pa yin des na rang
NK103(pe)020:742: don gtso bo ru sgrub pas sgo gsum gyi nyes
NK103(pe)020:744: sngon gyi 'phags pa dgra bcom pa'i rjes su slob pa ni spyod pa'o //
NK103(pe)020:747: 'das pa'i grong khyer du 'gro ba'i lam gyi rgyun la zhugs pas rgyun du zhugs pa dang /
NK103(pe)020:748: 'dod khams kyi lha mir lan re skye bas lan cig phyir 'ong ba dang /
NK103(pe)020:751: khams gsum gyi sred pa zad pas 'dod chags can
NK103(pe)020:752: thams cad kyis mchod par 'os pas dgra bcom pa
NK103(pe)020:753: dang bzhi las gsum gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu dang
NK103(pe)020:754: dgra bcom mthar thug tu 'gyur te /
NK103(pe)020:756: 'bras klang rgyur zhugs pa dang 'bras bur gnas pa gnyis gnyis su phye bas ni //
NK103(pe)020:757: zung gzhi la ya ba brgyad ni lus rgyan cha dang bral //
NK103(pe)020:759: dgra bcom pa la yang khams gsum gyi nyon mongs
NK103(pe)020:760: pa zad kyang lus ma dor pa'i lhag bcas dang
NK103(pe)020:761: / phung po lnga car 'gags pa'i lhag med kyi mya ngan las 'das pa ste /
NK103(pe)020:762: lus med gzung 'dzin phra ba tsam mo zhes 'bras klong las yod par ni gsungs so //
NK103(pe)020:765: rags pa la bsgribs ma bsgribs la sogs pa gzhigs
NK103(pe)020:766: phra ba la phyogs chas gzhigs te cha med blos
NK103(pe)020:767: gzhig pa las 'das pa'i gzung ba mi gnas pas
NK103(pe)020:768: / de la 'dzin pa'i skad cig ma'ang bden pa
NK103(pe)020:769: min lung drang lung nges lung gnyis gsungs pa las
NK103(pe)020:770: / / nang pa rang gi rgyal ba'i lung las
NK103(pe)020:771: rdul phran dang skad cig ma gnyis kyi don grub
NK103(pe)020:772: / / par gsungs pa / theg pa gong ma
NK103(pe)020:773: la 'jug pa'i lam stegs drang don tsam las nges
NK103(pe)020:776: mya ngan 'das pa yang ma thob par gsungs te /
NK103(pe)020:779: des na chags thogs med pa'i ye shes kyi gzigs pa mnga' ba'i sangs rgyas ma thob par /
NK103(pe)020:780: sgrib pa thams cad las grol ba'i mtshan nyid mya
NK103(pe)020:781: ngan las 'das pa'i dbyings rtogs pa mi 'thob ste
NK103(pe)020:783: 'od dang 'od zer spangs nas ma mthong bas ni
NK103(pe)020:784: nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor blta bar mi nus pa bzhin
NK103(pe)020:786: dge bshes la mi ltos par rang gis 'bras bu
NK103(pe)020:787: byang chub thob par kyi dod pa'i lta ba ni
NK103(pe)020:788: / b+hi b+hi sha na lung bstan pa'i mdo /
NK103(pe)020:789: rgyu la 'bras bu rten cing rgyu'i rjes su 'bras
NK103(pe)020:790: bu 'brel bar 'byung ba zab mo sgyu ma lta
NK103(pe)020:791: bu'i mtshan nyid du mthong ba dang /
NK103(pe)020:792: chos kyi dbyings mtha' dang dbus med par brjod pa dang bral ba'i don rtogs pa'o //
NK103(pe)020:794: yo ga tsaru'i t+ai ka las /
NK103(pe)020:795: gzugs kyi phung po las gzung ba'i chos la bdag med rtogs /
NK103(pe)020:799: dge bshes la mi slob par rang gi rig pas rtogs pas rang rgyal /
NK103(pe)020:802: de yang shes rab kyi dbang po rnon po ste
NK103(pe)020:803: nyan thos las lta spyod khyad par du 'phags kyang
NK103(pe)020:804: / 'on kyang brjod du med do snyam du 'du
NK103(pe)020:805: shes 'jug pas 'dzin pa chos kyi bdag ni nges
NK103(pe)020:806: par yod pa nyid du lta'o //
NK103(pe)020:809: bcu gnyis kyi dang po ma rig pa brgyad pa sred pa dang dgu pa len pa gsum rgyu //
NK103(pe)020:810: gnyis pa 'du byed dang bcu pa srid pa gnyis rkyen du gnas te //
NK103(pe)020:818: bdun po 'bras bu sdug bsngal nyid du grub pas //
NK103(pe)020:819: rgyu ma rig pa nas bkag pa ni 'bras bu yid sbyin bde ba'i mchog /
NK103(pe)020:821: spyod pa spyir nyan thos dang 'dra ni /
NK103(pe)020:823: stod nas me 'bar ba smad nas chu 'brug pa
NK103(pe)020:824: la sogs pa spyod pa lus kyi rdzu 'phrul sna
NK103(pe)020:825: tshogs gyis // gzhan gyi don shas 'ga' tsam spyod pa'o //
NK103(pe)020:828: dbang po rnon po bse ru lta bu gcig pur
NK103(pe)020:829: gnas pa dang rtul po gzhan la ltos pas sde
NK103(pe)020:830: dang khyus gnas pa tshogs na spyod pa gnyis te
NK103(pe)020:831: / mthar yid sbyin bde ba mchog gi sa thob bo zhes 'byung ngo //
NK103(pe)020:834: gzung ba'i yul bden par yod pa min kyang 'dzin pa yod par lta na /
NK103(pe)020:835: yul med pas shes pa de gang la nges par 'dzin pa gdung chad pa'i sras bzhin du /
NK103(pe)020:836: rigs pas 'thad pa'i 'dzin pa yod pa ma yin no //
NK103(pe)020:838: byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa ni /
NK103(pe)020:839: mdo sde rgyan las bsdus pa /
NK103(pe)020:840: theg pa chen po mdo sde mtha' yas la /
NK103(pe)020:842: rang gzhan gyi don sgrub pas sgrub pa che /
NK103(pe)020:843: bdag med gnyis rtogs pas ye shes 1chen 111po dang /
NK103(pe)020:844: bskal pa grangs med gsum du dka' ba la sbyor bas brtson 'grus che /
NK103(pe)020:845: mtha' gnyis la mi gnas pas thabs la mkhas pa 1dang /
NK103(pe)020:846: sangs rgyas kyi yon tan dpag tu med pa 'grub
NK103(pe)020:847: pas grub pa 1'khor ba ji srid par sangs rgyas
NK103(pe)020:849: phrin las 1chen 1111po bdun dang ldan pas na /
NK103(pe)020:850: theg pa chen po zhes bya bar ni nges par brjod //
NK103(pe)020:852: mdor na bdag med gnyis rtogs pas shes rab dang
NK103(pe)020:853: gzhan don gtsor spyod kyi snying rje che ba'i theg
NK103(pe)020:855: theg chen de'i lta ba la yang dbu sems gnyis las /
NK103(pe)020:856: sems tsam las phyi rol gyi don 'gog pas pa ni /
NK103(pe)020:857: 'jig rten na grags pa dang bstan bcos las 'byung
NK103(pe)020:858: ba'i bdag dang srog dang skye ba po dang shed
NK103(pe)020:859: las skye ba la sogs pa /
NK103(pe)020:860: bdag tu brjod pa sna tshogs dang /
NK103(pe)020:861: phung khams skye mched la sogs pa /
NK103(pe)020:862: chos su nye bar 'dogs pa sna tshogs pa du ma dag ni /
NK103(pe)020:863: rnam par shes par gyur pa las phyi rol na don med la /
NK103(pe)020:864: gyur pa'i rnam shes de yang las kyis 'phangs pa'i 'bras bu rnam par smin pa kun gzhi dang /
NK103(pe)020:865: de la rtag tu ngar sems pa'i bdag nyon yid
NK103(pe)020:866: dang yul la so sor rnam par rig pa tshogs
NK103(pe)020:868: bdag dang chos su nyer 'dogs pa //
NK103(pe)020:869: sna tshogs dag ni gang byung ba //
NK103(pe)020:870: de ni rnam par shes par gyur //
NK103(pe)020:871: gyur pa de yang rnam pa gsum //
NK103(pe)020:872: rnam par smin dang ngar sems dang //
NK103(pe)020:873: yul la rnam par rig pa'o //
NK103(pe)020:874: zhes sum cu pa las so /
NK103(pe)020:875: zhes sum cu pa las 'byung la /
NK103(pe)020:876: tshogs brgyad po de dag sems las byung ba nga
NK103(pe)020:877: gcig dang bcas pas rnam par brtags pa'i yul phyi
NK103(pe)020:878: snod dang / yang dag ma yin kun rtog ni /
NK103(pe)020:879: sems dang sems byung zhes drang /
NK103(pe)020:880: bdag dang phung po khams dang skye mched gzugs sgra la sogs pa'i dngos po de dag med pas /
NK103(pe)020:882: rnam par shes pa gyur pa 'di /
NK103(pe)020:883: rnam par rtog pa kho na yin te /
NK103(pe)020:884: dmigs pa med pa'i phyir khams gsum dang 'dus ma
NK103(pe)020:885: byas thams cad rnam par rig pa tsam ni de
NK103(pe)020:886: las lhag pa'i yul gcod pa'o //
NK103(pe)020:888: de nyid la ngo bo nyid kun brtags dang gzhan
NK103(pe)020:889: dbang dang yongs su grub pa'i mtshan nyid dang gsum
NK103(pe)020:890: gyi rnam par bzhag thams cad rnam par rig pa
NK103(pe)020:891: tsam / rnam rtog yin te de yis ni /
NK103(pe)020:892: rnam brtags de med des na 'di /
NK103(pe)020:895: de la yang phyi rol don gyi rnam par snang ba 'di /
NK103(pe)020:896: shes pa'i go bor bden par 'dod pa'i rnam pa bden par smra ba zhes ste /
NK103(pe)020:898: phyi rol gyi don med pa de phyir yul du
NK103(pe)020:899: snang ba 'di ni sems po las log pa'i shes
NK103(pe)020:900: pa yi myong ba rang bzhin du tha mi dad
NK103(pe)020:901: pa'i bdag nyid yin pas bdag shes par rung bas
NK103(pe)020:903: phyi rol don gyi rang bzhin du tha mi dad
NK103(pe)020:904: pa'i shes pa las gzhan du gyur pa dag la
NK103(pe)020:905: // shes de yis 'brel pa med pas don ji ltar shes par 'gyur //
NK103(pe)020:907: de la yang shes pa 'dra du ma mi skye
NK103(pe)020:908: bar bshad pas shes pa la snang dkar dmar du
NK103(pe)020:909: mar snang yang bden mig gi shes pa rdzas gcig
NK103(pe)020:910: gi rang bzhin tu bden par smra ba shes rab
NK103(pe)020:912: rnam pa dang shes pa tha mi dad pas rnam
NK103(pe)020:913: pa la grangs gcig dang du ma ji snyed yod
NK103(pe)020:914: pa bzhin shes pa'i grangs kyang gcig dang du ma
NK103(pe)020:915: de snyed du bden par slob dpon sh+aakya blo smra
NK103(pe)020:916: ba ste nang tshegs gnyis yin no zhes 'byung ngo
NK103(pe)020:917: // rnam pa brdzun par smra ba ni /
NK103(pe)020:918: gzugs la sogs don gyi rnam par snang ba rnams ni /
NK103(pe)020:919: kun shes gnyi gar mi bden par kun brtags dngos med brdzun par 'dod de /
NK103(pe)020:921: rab tu byed pa nyi shu pa /
NK103(pe)020:922: khams gsum po 'di dag chos can rnam par rig tsam nyid yin te bsgrub bya /
NK103(pe)020:923: bden par yod pa ma yin kyang don du snang ba'i phyir //
NK103(pe)020:924: dper na rab rib can gyi mig dag gis //
NK103(pe)020:925: nam mkhar skra shad dang zla ba gnyis la sogs pa med kyang mthong ba bzhin no //
NK103(pe)020:928: gshis dag kyang skye bo la 'khrul pa'i rnam pa
NK103(pe)020:929: sangs rgyas sa na yod pa dri ma dang bcas
NK103(pe)020:930: pa dang / rang rig la gzung 'dzin dri ma
NK103(pe)020:931: gdod nas med pa dag pa pa gnyis su 'dod
NK103(pe)020:932: pa dang / / ces kyang grag go //
NK103(pe)020:933: dbu ma pa'i lta ba ni /
NK103(pe)020:934: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad bden pa gnyis su 'dod de //
NK103(pe)020:937: tha snyad du snang 'jal gyi shes pa'i ngor /
NK103(pe)020:938: 'khrul pa'i blo la snang ba'i yul kun rdzob tsam la dbye na /
NK103(pe)020:939: rnam par rtog pas kun tu brtags pa dang rgyu
NK103(pe)020:940: rkyen gzhan gyi dbang ni ma dag pa gzung 'dzin
NK103(pe)020:942: dag pa 'jig rten pa'i ye shes yul ji snyed pa dang bcas pa'ang kun rdzob //
NK103(pe)020:943: snang ba la de dang mthun par don byed nus
NK103(pe)020:944: pa ni yang dag pa'i kun rdzob ste de la
NK103(pe)020:946: de spong byed kyii gnyen po tshogs sbyor mthong sgom mthar lam lnga dang /
NK103(pe)020:947: spangs pa'i 'bras bu ye shes bzhi dang sku gnyis kyang kun rdzob /
NK103(pe)020:948: snang ba tsam las don med pas grub mtha' ngan
NK103(pe)020:949: pas brtags pa'i rtog bcas 1dang dbang shes rtog med
NK103(pe)020:953: slob dpon zhi ba 'tsho kun rdzob tu phyi rol
NK103(pe)020:954: gyi don med par rnam par shes pa tsam du
NK103(pe)020:955: smra ba rnal 'byor spyod pa'i dbu ma dang /
NK103(pe)020:956: slob dpon b+ha bya dang ye shes snying po gnyis
NK103(pe)020:957: phyi nang gi dngos po thams cad rten cing 'brel
NK103(pe)020:958: bar 'byung ba sgyu ma tsam du yul sems tha
NK103(pe)020:959: dad du 'dod pa'i mdo sde spyod pa'i dbu ma
NK103(pe)020:960: gnyis kun rdzob cung zad mi mthun yang /
NK103(pe)020:962: dbu ma 'di gnyis kun rdzob tu cung zad mi mthun yang /
NK103(pe)020:963: zla ba grags pas 'jig rten grags ngo dang bstun no //
NK103(pe)020:964: don dam par phyi nang gi dngos po thams cad
NK103(pe)020:965: rang bzhin med par 'dod du gsum ka /'dra bas
NK103(pe)020:968: yang dag pa'i kun rdzob de dag kyang chos nyid lam rim las /
NK103(pe)020:969: sgyu ma lta bu rkyen las skyes //
NK103(pe)020:970: phral snang bya ba kun kyang byed //
NK103(pe)020:971: rtog can rnams la mthun par tshad //
NK103(pe)020:972: gzugs brnyan 'dra phyir brtags na dben //
NK103(pe)020:973: de phyir thams cad sgyu ma tsam //
NK103(pe)020:975: yang dag pa'i don mthong ba la bsgribs pas de skad du kun rdzob ces bya'o //
NK103(pe)020:978: brtags pa'i skye ba la sogs pas stong pa rnam
NK103(pe)020:979: grangs kyi don dam pa ni rigs pa'i shes pas
NK103(pe)020:980: snang ba la gzhigs pas spros pa phyogs res stong
NK103(pe)020:981: pa'o // brtags pa'i spros pa'i mtha' thams cad las
NK103(pe)020:982: grol ba'i stong nyid rnam grangs ma yin pa'i don
NK103(pe)020:984: shes byed rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes kyi yul du gyur pa las /
NK103(pe)020:988: 'gro 'ong la sogs spros 4pa brgyad dang bral ba la /
NK103(pe)020:989: yul dang yul can du rtog bcas kyi shes pas brtags kyang /
NK103(pe)020:990: don gyi ngo bo nyid la smra brjod kyi mtha' las 'das pa'i stong pa nyid yin /
NK103(pe)020:992: de ltar gzhi ma grub pa la khyad par gyi chos mi 'dra ba'i dbye ba med de /
NK103(pe)020:994: chos nyid shes pa dam pa'i yul don gyi bden pa de la /
NK103(pe)020:995: grangs kyi dbye ba'i spros pa nye bar zhi ba yin /
NK103(pe)020:999: shes par bya ba'i yul gyi mchog tu gyur pa don gyi dam pa shes rab dam pa yi /
NK103(pe)020:1000: yul yin bas dam pa'i don rtog ge ba'i yul ma yin gyi /
NK103(pe)020:1001: mi slu ba dang nges pa'i phyir bden pa'i sgra 'jug go //
NK103(pe)020:1003: sgyu ma rigs grub pa dang stong pa nyid la
NK103(pe)020:1004: zhen pa'i mtshan mar smra ba ni dbu ma chen
NK103(pe)020:1005: po'i dgongs pa ma yin no //
NK103(pe)020:1007: dbu sems de dag gi ting nge 'dzin ni bsod nams kyi tshogs sogs pas tshogs lam du lus /
NK103(pe)020:1010: chos dran chung ngu pa ni mtshan nyid ma nor
NK103(pe)020:1011: bar shes pa'i lhag mthong nye bar gzhag pa ni
NK103(pe)020:1012: de nyid la rtse gcig tu 'jog pa'i zhi gnas
NK103(pe)020:1013: bzhi dang / 'bring po yang dag par spong ba
NK103(pe)020:1014: brtson 'grus kyi rang bzhin bzhi dge ba ma skyes
NK103(pe)020:1015: bzhi dang / pa skyed / skyes pa spel /
NK103(pe)020:1016: sdig pa ma skyes pa mi skyed /
NK103(pe)020:1018: rdzu 'phrul gyi mngon shes lnga la der 'gro ba'i
NK103(pe)020:1019: rgyu yin pas rkang pa bzhi sgom mos dang brtson
NK103(pe)020:1021: mos pa spyod pa'i sa sbyor ba'i lam du thar
NK103(pe)020:1022: pa cha mthun gyi dge ba la dbang bas dbang
NK103(pe)020:1023: po dad brtson dran pa ting 'dzin shes rab ni
NK103(pe)020:1024: / lngas snang ba thob pas drod dang mched pa rtse mor gnas la //
NK103(pe)020:1025: mi mthun pas mi nyams pas stobs lngas don gyi
NK103(pe)020:1026: phyogs gcig la zhugs pas bzod pa dang 'jig rten
NK103(pe)020:1027: de ma thag pa chos mchog tu gyur te /
NK103(pe)020:1028: lam de gnyis lta ba bden gnyis kyi don spyi'i
NK103(pe)020:1029: rnam pa tsam la dmigs pas zhi gnas 'ba' zhig
NK103(pe)020:1030: sgom pa la / bskal pa grangs med pa gcig gis mthong lam la sbyor bas sbyor lam ro //
NK103(pe)020:1031: mthong lam thams cad stong nyid du rtogs pa'i rnam
NK103(pe)020:1032: par mi rtog pa'i ye shes ni chos rnam par
NK103(pe)020:1034: sa dang po rab tu dga' ba'i sa la gnas
NK103(pe)020:1035: pa'i tshe byang chub ces bya ste gtso bo dang
NK103(pe)020:1037: kyi yan lag bdun dran pa dang /
NK103(pe)020:1043: btang snyoms bdun dang ldan la //
NK103(pe)020:1044: sa gnyis pa nas dri ma med pa /
NK103(pe)020:1049: ring du song ba brgyad pa mi g.yo ba'i bar
NK103(pe)020:1050: mthong spang sgom spang ring du spangs pas 'phags pa'i
NK103(pe)020:1051: der 'gro ba'i sgo'am rgyu la lam gyi yan lag
NK103(pe)020:1060: sdug bsngal la sogs pa 'phags pa'i bden pa bzhi
NK103(pe)020:1061: dang bsam gtan bzhi dang tshad med pa bzhi snyoms
NK103(pe)020:1062: 'jug bzhi / rnam par thar pa brgyad /
NK103(pe)020:1064: la sogs pa yang lam gyi grogs tsam du gnas so //
NK103(pe)020:1065: mthong sgom gyi lam po de dag la yang bskal
NK103(pe)020:1066: pa grangs med gcig gis sgrib par rag pa sbyong
NK103(pe)020:1067: ngo // sa brgyad pa dang sa dgu pa legs
NK103(pe)020:1068: pa'i blo gros dang bcu pa chos kyi sprin la
NK103(pe)020:1069: ngo // gnas pa'i tshe / de bzhin gshegs pa
NK103(pe)020:1070: longs sku'i zhal bstan pa dang phyag gis spyi bor
NK103(pe)020:1072: 'tshang rgya ba la gang gis kyang bar chad pa
NK103(pe)020:1073: med pa'i lam gnyen po gzhan med pas rdo rje
NK103(pe)020:1074: lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin dri med dam pa'i shes
NK103(pe)020:1075: rab gyis shes bya thams cad mkhyen pa kho na
NK103(pe)020:1076: la sgrib pa shin tu cha phra ba de bskal
NK103(pe)020:1077: pa grangs med pa gcig gis rgyun bcad nas sangs
NK103(pe)020:1078: rgyas kyi sa thob pa ni bdag gzhan gyi don
NK103(pe)020:1081: sdom pa nyi shu pa las /
NK103(pe)020:1082: 'gro ba 'dul ba'i rkyen du 'tsham par bzhin du tshar mi gcod pa dang /
NK103(pe)020:1083: rdzu 'phrul bstan nas srid bsdigs pa sogs pa sbyor
NK103(pe)020:1084: ba dam pa min pas 'dul bzhin du mi byed
NK103(pe)020:1086: bsam pa snying rjer ldan pa'i phyir dang byams pa'i phyir dang /
NK103(pe)020:1087: sems dge ba la dge sdig gang spyad kyang nyams pa'i nyes pa med /
NK103(pe)020:1091: thabs byams snying rje chen po rnams dang ldan pa la //
NK103(pe)020:1092: nyon mongs pa spyod pa nyid byang chub thob pa'i yan lag tu 'gyur //
NK103(pe)020:1095: thugs rje chen po mnga' ba'i gdul bya ring ba
NK103(pe)020:1096: pha rol gzigs pas nyan thos la bkag pa rnams
NK103(pe)020:1097: kyang byang chub sems dpa' de la gnang /
NK103(pe)020:1099: mdor bsdu na ci byed kyang snying rjes gzhi bzung nas spyod pa'o //
NK103(pe)020:1102: sku gsum chos longs sprul ye shes me /
NK103(pe)020:1106: bzhi yi bdag nyid yin de /
NK103(pe)020:1107: chos sku mnyam par bzhag pa la gzugs sku gnyis kyi rjes thob kyi tshul du gnas pa'am /
NK103(pe)020:1108: sangs rgyas mnyam bzhag 'ba' zhig tsam yin la gzugs
NK103(pe)020:1109: sku gnyis po 'dul bya 'khor gyi blo la snang
NK103(pe)020:1111: chos kyi dbyings spros pa thams cad dang bral ba
NK103(pe)020:1112: nyid tsam zhig chos sku yin la gzugs sku gnyis
NK103(pe)020:1113: de 0bzhin / kun rdzob sgyu ma tsam du rang
NK103(pe)020:1114: snang gi ye shes gnas par 'dod pa'ang 'khor gyi
NK103(pe)020:1115: de 0bzhin / snang ba de'i / sgrib pa thams
NK103(pe)020:1116: cad spangs pas kun tu 'od kyi sa ste de
NK103(pe)020:1118: zhes dga' rab kyis gsungs pa bzhin no //
NK103(pe)020:1120: sems tsam pa myong ba gnyis med kyi shes pa
NK103(pe)020:1121: rang rig rang gsal don dam pa'i bden par 'dod
NK103(pe)020:1125: rang rig gzhan dbang las skye ba de yang rtag
NK103(pe)020:1126: pa las skye'am mi rtag pa las skye bar 'gyur
NK103(pe)020:1129: rim dang cig car du brtags pas /
NK103(pe)020:1131: mi rtag pa las skye na /
NK103(pe)020:1132: dus gsum gyi 'das pa las skye'am ma 'ongs pa las skye /
NK103(pe)020:1133: 'das pa las skye na zhig nas med pas skyed byed kyi rgyu min /
NK103(pe)020:1134: ma 'ongs pa las skye na ma skyes pas med
NK103(pe)020:1135: pa de dang 'dra ste dngos med de gnyis kyis
NK103(pe)020:1136: / da ltar ba la phan ma btags pas rgyu min no //
NK103(pe)020:1137: gal te rgyu snga ma ma zhig la skad cig
NK103(pe)020:1138: ma gzhan gyis bar ma chod par 'bras bu da
NK103(pe)020:1139: ltar ba skye 'o zhe na bdag nyid thams cad
NK103(pe)020:1141: phyogs gcig gis bar ma chod /
NK103(pe)020:1143: de yang skad cig ma snga ma 'gags pa'i dus
NK103(pe)020:1144: na da ltar ba rang rang skye ba'i phyogs kyi
NK103(pe)020:1145: dus dang / skad cig ma phyi ma skyed pa'i
NK103(pe)020:1146: dus su da ltar rang 'gag pa'i phyogs kyi dus
NK103(pe)020:1147: dus dang / dang cha gnyis / ldan te phyogs
NK103(pe)020:1148: gcig gis ma chod na dus cha yod pa de
NK103(pe)020:1149: rgyun yin gyi dus matha'i skad cig ma'i ming gi
NK103(pe)020:1152: dang po ltar na sngar gyi rgyu 'gag dus kyi da ltar ba rang skye ba'i phyogs dang /
NK103(pe)020:1153: 'bras bu phyis skye dus kyi da ltar ba rang
NK103(pe)020:1154: 'gag pa'i phyogs gnyis gcig ste bdag nyid thams cad
NK103(pe)020:1155: kyis ma chod na de bzhin du snga phyi thams
NK103(pe)020:1156: cad dus matha'i skad cig gcig la thim par 'gyur
NK103(pe)020:1157: bas dus rgyun 'chad de bskal pa yang skad cig
NK103(pe)020:1159: nges don gyi mdo zab cing rgya che ba las
NK103(pe)020:1160: skye 'gag gi rgyun las grol ba'i ye shes basngagasa
NK103(pe)020:1161: / 'phags pa rigs pa can yab sras gyis dngos por lta ba la shin tu smad /
NK103(pe)020:1162: rtag tu skye chos rnams thams cad de bzhin gshegs dang 'dra /
NK103(pe)020:1163: byis pa'i blo can mtshan mar 'dzin pa dag /'jig rten dag na med pa'i chos la spyod /
NK103(pe)020:1164: ces de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi yul la
NK103(pe)020:1165: 'jug pa ye shes snang ba rgyan gyi mdo las
NK103(pe)020:1168: blo yis dngos po la rnam par gzhigs na ni /
NK103(pe)020:1169: rgyu rkyen gzhan gyi dbang gis skye ba med cing kun tu brtags pa 'ang med /
NK103(pe)020:1170: yongs su grub pa'i dngos po yang bden par med na /
NK103(pe)020:1171: zhes pa rang bzhin med ngo cing rnam rig shes drugmed //
NK103(pe)020:1172: dngos nyon po med cing kun gzhi med //
NK103(pe)020:1173: ro mtshungs byis pa rtog ge ba //
NK103(pe)020:1174: ngan pa rnams kyis 'di dag brtags //
NK103(pe)020:1175: mtshan zhi ma'i dngos po rnam rig shes dang //
NK103(pe)020:1176: nyon yid kyis g.yo ba gang yin las //
NK103(pe)020:1177: nga yi sras rnams rab 'das nas //
NK103(pe)020:1178: de dag rnam par mi rtog dpyod //
NK103(pe)020:1181: dbu ma pa'i kun rdzob kyi bden pa mi 'thad pa ni /
NK103(pe)020:1183: lam dang 'bras bu ye shes kun rdzob tu 'dod
NK103(pe)020:1184: pa ni kun rdzob kyi mtshan nyid dang lam 'bras
NK103(pe)020:1186: des na yang dag pa'i don la rdzob cing nges
NK103(pe)020:1187: pa'i don la sgrib pa'i phyir mtshan nyid de dang
NK103(pe)020:1188: / mthong lam des rtogs nas sgom lam nges don
NK103(pe)020:1189: la gnas par 'dod pa de gnyis gcig tu ga
NK103(pe)020:1192: gshis kyi chos nyid spros pa'i mtha' dang bral ba'i
NK103(pe)020:1193: ngang tshul yin pa der grol ba sangs rgyas su
NK103(pe)020:1194: bzung ba / de ltar du bden na dang po
NK103(pe)020:1195: 'khrul snang 'char ba'i rten rang snang yang med par
NK103(pe)020:1196: bzung ba / zad / spros bral de 'jal ba'i
NK103(pe)020:1197: rigs pa'ang mi rnyed la ye shes de rgyun gcod
NK103(pe)020:1198: bzung ba / zad / pa'i / gnyen po'ang mi
NK103(pe)020:1199: 'thad la sangs kyi ye shes med na lung yang
NK103(pe)020:1200: bzung ba / zad / pa'i / brdzun par 'gyur
NK103(pe)020:1201: / 'gro ba'i don nus pa'i gzhi chos sku la
NK103(pe)020:1202: bkag pas theg dman nyan rang gi 'dod pa dang
NK103(pe)020:1203: bzung ba / zad / pa'i / brdzun par 'gyur
NK103(pe)020:1204: / mtshungs par ldan / sngon lam du smon lam
NK103(pe)020:1205: btab pa dang sems bskyed pa dang mos tsam gyis
NK103(pe)020:1206: 'gro don de 'grub par 'dod pas nyan rang dang
NK103(pe)020:1208: deng sang 'gro ba thams cad rgyun chad par thal /
NK103(pe)020:1209: sems can bsgral bar dam bcas pa'i smon lam mi 'grub pa'o //
NK103(pe)020:1210: dngos su chad par lta ba khas blangs so //
NK103(pe)020:1211: 'dir zhen pa'i stong pa nyid kyi 'dam las sngar su'ang ma thon /
NK103(pe)020:1213: dbu sems de dag gi 'bras bu yang mthar thug gi 'bras bu ma yin te /
NK103(pe)020:1215: mtshan nyid pas bskal pa grangs med du bsgrubs pas
NK103(pe)020:1216: grub pa'i 'bras bu kun tu 'od kyi sa ni
NK103(pe)020:1217: / theg pa chen po gsang sngags kyi bsti gnas tsam gyi sa ru bstan /
NK103(pe)020:1219: de dag las rdo rje'i theg pa khyad par go ba myur bul /
NK103(pe)020:1222: mchan matha'i skyon gyis gos ma gos /
NK103(pe)020:1223: nyams su len tshul chos nyid yul du byed mi byed /
NK103(pe)020:1224: gdul bya la dbang po rno rtul /
NK103(pe)020:1226: 'bras bu la gnas skabs mthar thug /
NK103(pe)020:1227: gzhung legs par brtags te don gsal bar ston mi ston dang /
NK103(pe)020:1237: 'bras bu rdo rje'i ming gi khyad par lnga yis 'phags par mkhas pa nya ri /
NK103(pe)020:1238: rngod phu ba dag gis gsungs kyang /
NK103(pe)020:1239: dbu sems dang kri yog yan chad kyi khyad par yin /
NK103(pe)020:1241: mdor bsdu na don dam pa rang bzhin ci yang ma yin pa las /
NK103(pe)020:1242: slob dpon pad+mas thabs zhags kyi 'grel par /
NK103(pe)020:1243: chos thams cad mtshan ma med pa las byung bas don dam pa ni rgyu'o //
NK103(pe)020:1244: sgyu ma tsam du snang bas kun rdzob ni 'bras bu yin par rig par bya'o //
NK103(pe)020:1247: bzhin 'gyur bzhin las g.yos med ltar //
NK103(pe)020:1248: kun dngos rig pa cir snang phyir //
NK103(pe)020:1249: ngo bo nyid kyi rgyu ru gcig /
NK103(pe)020:1251: chos thams cad kyi ngo bo nyid kyi rgyur lhun
NK103(pe)020:1252: gyis grub pas dngos stong gi mthar ma lhungs pa
NK103(pe)020:1254: thams cad dag ces bya ba yang /
NK103(pe)020:1255: dngos po bsal dag ma yin te /
NK103(pe)020:1256: snang spyod nyid na rnam par dag /
NK103(pe)020:1257: de phyir kun rdzob brdzun mi blta /
NK103(pe)020:1259: de nyid cir yang mi 'gag par lha'i dkyil 'khor la sogs par snang bas /
NK103(pe)020:1260: kun rdzob 'khrul pa'i mthar ma lhungs pas khyad par du gyur pa'o //
NK103(pe)020:1261: rdo rje'i theg pa de la phyi nang gnyis las
NK103(pe)020:1262: lta spyod sgrub pas phyi pa 'dul sdom thub par
NK103(pe)020:1263: srung pa rgyud la gsum gyi //
NK103(pe)020:1264: dang po lus ngag gi bya ba gtsor ston pas kri ya pa ni /
NK103(pe)020:1265: don dam pa dag pa'i chos nyid yod med rtag
NK103(pe)020:1266: chad kyi mtha' bzhi'i spros pa dang bral ba la
NK103(pe)020:1271: ye shes bzhi'i yon tan rigs de /
NK103(pe)020:1274: gsum gyi ye shes dal ye shes pa /
NK103(pe)020:1275: rje bo dam tshig pa 'bangs kyi tshul du lta ba'o //
NK103(pe)020:1276: ting nge 'dzin gyis dam tshig pa mtshan bshen gsum /
NK103(pe)020:1285: sku yongs rdzogs dang rje lha drug dang ldan par bskyed de /
NK103(pe)020:1287: ye shes can rje bo'i tshul du spyan drangs te /
NK103(pe)020:1288: mkha' yi rten gzugs brnyan la phyag rgya bzhis gzud /
NK103(pe)020:1289: de la gtsang ma'i mchod pa lnga'am bdun gyis mchod la mnyam bzhag ste /
NK103(pe)020:1290: bdag lha 'phro 'du'i gsal ba gsum dang ldan pas sngags bzlas pa'i skyon rngam klog las /
NK103(pe)020:1291: sgra che ma yin chung ba min //
NK103(pe)020:1292: mgyogs par yin bul bar min //
NK103(pe)020:1293: drag par ma yin dal bar min //
NK103(pe)020:1294: yig 'bru yan lag nyams pa min //
NK103(pe)020:1295: yengs min glal sagosa bar ma chod //
NK103(pe)020:1296: rgyu ba'i sems pa spangs pa dang //
NK103(pe)020:1299: thun mtshams su ye shes sems dpa' la mchod pa
NK103(pe)020:1300: dang bstod pa dang bshags pa la sogs zin pa
NK103(pe)020:1301: dang lha ye shes pa gshegs su gsol la /
NK103(pe)020:1302: dam tshig pa'i dkyil 'khor bsdus nas rnal 'byor pa'i spyod lam ci bder gnas par bya /
NK103(pe)020:1303: zhes 'byung ba bzhin du ye shes pa'i bya ba rnams so //
NK103(pe)020:1304: de yang spyod pa lus ngag gi bya byed gtso bor len te /
NK103(pe)020:1305: bya ba la gtsor byed pa'i lam pas ma smas
NK103(pe)020:1306: pa gtsang ma'i kha zas 0dkar gsum la sogs pa
NK103(pe)020:1307: / ras gtsang ma kha dog tshon gyis bsgyur ba'i
NK103(pe)020:1308: gos gyon de yang yar ngo'i tshes brgyad la sogs
NK103(pe)020:1310: gza' 1phur bu dar ba dang rgyu skar 1rgyal ba sogs bzang 11ba'i tshe lha'i gzugs brnyan 0dang /
NK103(pe)020:1311: sbags btsog med par gtsang ma'i mchod pa yo byad 00bsogs 00nas gdong la sogs pa khrus byas te /
NK103(pe)020:1314: don dam pa stong pa nyid las kun rdzob tu
NK103(pe)020:1315: yul rnam snang dang yul can nam mi bskyod pa
NK103(pe)020:1316: bya ba rin 'byung byed pa don grub gang rung
NK103(pe)020:1317: bsdus pa'i lha rigs bzhi la ye shes pa dpon
NK103(pe)020:1318: dam tshig pa g.yog gi tshul tu byin rlabs snang
NK103(pe)020:1319: bar lta ba tsam mi mthun pa las gong ma
NK103(pe)020:1320: yo ga 'og ma kri ya gnyis dang mthun te
NK103(pe)020:1322: gnyi ga dang mthun par spyod pa'i rgyud kyis bya ba dang rnal 'byor pa /
NK103(pe)020:1323: gnyi ga'i mthu las 'bras bu grub par 'dod pa yin zhe'o //
NK103(pe)020:1324: yo ga pa'i lta ba ni /
NK103(pe)020:1325: don dam par rnam par snang mdzad chen po stong pa nyid du 'dod la /
NK103(pe)020:1326: kun rdzob tu snang ba 'di chos kyi dbyings kyi byin rlabs lha rigs lnga'i dkyil 'khor yin te /
NK103(pe)020:1327: de ltar ting nge 'dzin gsal na ye shes pa
NK103(pe)020:1328: dang dam tshig pa grogs po'i tshul du tha dad
NK103(pe)020:1329: la bzang ngan med par lta'o //
NK103(pe)020:1330: mngon par byang chub pa lnga dang cho 'phrul bzhi
NK103(pe)020:1331: yan lag dgu ldan gyi bsam gtan gyi sgo nas
NK103(pe)020:1332: / 'phags pa'i gzugs kyi sku phyag rgya bzhi dam tshig thugs /
NK103(pe)020:1335: sku phyag rgya chen po dang ldan pa'i rnal 'byor gyis 'bras bu grub ste /
NK103(pe)020:1336: bden pa gnyis snang stong res 'jog tu nyams su
NK103(pe)020:1337: len cing lus ngag gi bya byed la gtso bor
NK103(pe)020:1338: mi spyod do // phyi rgyud gsum po de dag gi 'bras bu ni /
NK103(pe)020:1340: don dam par spros pa dang bral ba de mngon
NK103(pe)020:1341: du byas pa ni chos kyi sku yin la kun
NK103(pe)020:1342: rdzob lha'i dkyil 'khor mtshan dang dpe byad du bstan
NK103(pe)020:1343: pa mngon du byas pa ni longs spyod rdzogs pa'i
NK103(pe)020:1344: sku la / thugs rjes 'gro ba'i don du sna
NK103(pe)020:1345: tshogs su sprul ste gdul bya'i ngor cir yang shar
NK103(pe)020:1348: longs sku de la yang kri ya pa rigs gsum rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sa dang /
NK103(pe)020:1349: u pa ya rigs bzhi rdo rje 'chang ba dang /
NK103(pe)020:1350: yo ga pa rigs lnga srab car du ma gyur
NK103(pe)020:1351: pas stug po bkod pa'i sa'i bye brag kyang yod
NK103(pe)020:1352: do // de dag sun dbyung ba ni /
NK103(pe)020:1354: kun rdzob tu lha ye shes pa dang bdag dam tshig pa gnyis rje khol du lta /
NK103(pe)020:1355: chos nyid kyi yon tan gyi ngang la bzang ngan
NK103(pe)020:1356: yod par 'gyur he ruhdang khyab pa khas blangs 'dod
NK103(pe)020:1357: na don dam rang bzhin gyis matha'i dri ma dag
NK103(pe)020:1358: par gcig par mi rung la /
NK103(pe)020:1359: kun rdzob dang don dam gnyis tha dad du 'dod ce na /
NK103(pe)020:1360: kun rdzob lha'i dal yang ye shes kyi sku min
NK103(pe)020:1361: par thal te don dam las tha dad pa'i phyir
NK103(pe)020:1362: ro // de yang 'dod na bsgoms pas kyang 'bras
NK103(pe)020:1363: bu snang bar mi rigs te bsgoms pa don med
NK103(pe)020:1365: dam tshig pa dang ye shes pa grogs po'i tshul du lta bar byed pas /
NK103(pe)020:1366: lha dang bdag tu tha dad du 'dod de chos can /
NK103(pe)020:1367: bdag gcig pa'i 'brel pa med pas ye shes pa bsgrubs kyang mi 'grub par thal ba dang /
NK103(pe)020:1368: tha dad pa des na don dam nyid la yang skyon yod pa ni /
NK103(pe)020:1369: don dam chos can gnyis pa yod par 'gyur gal te skyon de med de gcig go ce na /
NK103(pe)020:1370: rang gcig pu la grogs su lta bar mi rigs te grogs su 'dod pa'i dam bca' bud /
NK103(pe)020:1373: gdod ma nas phyogs bcu dus bzhi rgyal ba'i ngo bo nyid du lhun gyis grub ste /
NK103(pe)020:1374: k+aa b+aa tsi mi zad par rgyan gyi 'khor lo ru rang snang ba'i don de /
NK103(pe)020:1375: ma mthong bas rmongs pa'i 'khrul pa rnams /
NK103(pe)020:1376: brgyud pa'i byin rlabs yo ga lha dang kri ya yon tan lhar /
NK103(pe)020:1377: snang bar 'dod cing bden pa res 'jog tu sems
NK103(pe)020:1378: shing sgom par 'dod pa la sogs spyod pa blang
NK103(pe)020:1379: dor theg pa gzhan las 'phags par 'dod pa ni
NK103(pe)020:1381: dper na mig mdongs bas nam mkha' la 'dom gyis brnyabs kyang mi rnyogs pa bzhin du /
NK103(pe)020:1382: nor ba'i lam gyis ma nor rnyed mi 'gyur //
NK103(pe)020:1385: kri ya pa rigs gsum dang yo ga pa rigs lngar 'dod pa dag ni /
NK103(pe)020:1386: lta bas bdag nyid chen po dbyer med kyi don ma rtogs pa'i phyir /
NK103(pe)020:1387: thun mong gi mnyam pa yin par in+d+ra b+hu ti nga smra'o //
NK103(pe)020:1390: snang stong res 'jog gi bsam gtan gyis 'bras bu gcig sgrub pa ni /
NK103(pe)020:1391: dper na tsha reg dang grang reg tha dad pa gcig tu bsdus nas //
NK103(pe)020:1392: 'bras bu gtso bsreg phyogs gcig sgrub par 'dod pa'i blun po dang 'dra //
NK103(pe)020:1395: lam gyi rtsol bas ngal ba rnams /
NK103(pe)020:1396: brod pa bskyed pa'i phyir kun tu 'od dang /
NK103(pe)020:1397: rdo rje 'dzin stug po bkod pa'i sa rnams 'bras
NK103(pe)020:1398: bu yin par bstan pa yin gyi mthar thug pa
NK103(pe)020:1399: ma yin no // ces gsungs so //
NK103(pe)020:1401: bdag dang lha sems kyi cho 'phrul lam rtsal dang
NK103(pe)020:1402: rang 'od du 'dod pas tha mi dad par lta
NK103(pe)020:1403: ba 0dang / des 0na dngos grub rang las 'byung ba dang /
NK103(pe)020:1404: byang sems dri chen la sogs pa dam rdzas lnga la rdzogs par spyod pas phyi pa las /
NK103(pe)020:1405: kha yar ba la phyi pa'ang spyod par gsungs khyad par du 'phags so //
NK103(pe)020:1407: bskyed pa gtsor ston pa ma h+aa yo ga'i lta ba ni /
NK103(pe)020:1408: don dam par rig pa spros bral la 'phags pa'i dkor lam rim las /
NK103(pe)020:1409: don mchog lnga 'bras ye shes dbyings //
NK103(pe)020:1410: bdun dang gsum phyir don dam pa //
NK103(pe)020:1412: bdun lhun gyis grub pa dang /
NK103(pe)020:1414: don dam du ni dkor bdun la //
NK103(pe)020:1415: kun rdzob tu ni mnyam rdzogs so //
NK103(pe)020:1417: chos thams cad rang rig pa'i sku dang ye shes
NK103(pe)020:1418: su gsal ba la 'bras bu lus pa med par
NK103(pe)020:1419: rdzogs pa'o // de gnyis re mos su brjod kyang dbyer /
NK103(pe)020:1421: 'jig rten brtan g.yo la sogs pa //
NK103(pe)020:1422: snang ba nyid na ngo bo med //
NK103(pe)020:1423: de nyid chos sku chen po yin /
NK103(pe)020:1424: med kyi ngo bor sangs rgyas par 'dod de //
NK103(pe)020:1425: gdul bya'i mos pa dang sbyangs pa tha dad nyon
NK103(pe)020:1426: mongs pa dang shes rab che chung gi snang bas
NK103(pe)020:1427: lam gnyis su ye shes gsang ba las /
NK103(pe)020:1428: thabs gnyis lam dang grol yin te /
NK103(pe)020:1429: phye ba'i thabs lam la gnyis las cig car ba ni /
NK103(pe)020:1430: ye nas lhan skyes pa'i ye shes su lhun gyis grub pas /
NK103(pe)020:1431: ri mo'i lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor la

NK103(pe)020:1513: kyang / der zhen nas sgro 'dogs na gong gi

NK103(pe)020:1515: nas gdags pas khyad ci yang med la khyed kyi
NK103(pe)020:1516: gnyis med phyogs gcig tu bzung ba la gshis la

NK103(pe)020:1530: don la bde ba'i dngos por 'dzin pa'i zhen par gnas //
NK103(pe)020:1534: rang sa'i 'bras bu thob kyang bcos ma'i sa /

NK103(pe)020:1536: te 'di'i don la 'jug dgos pa 'dra ba'i phyir
NK103(pe)020:1538: a nu yo ga'i lta ba ni /

NK103(pe)020:1543: yum kun tu bzang mo zhes /

NK103(pe)020:1546: grub pa'i dkyil 'khor rig pa'i ye shes yab /

NK103(pe)020:1548: ba byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor gyi dbyings ye

NK103(pe)020:1552: sangs rgyas nyid de ye shes sku //
NK103(pe)020:1553: thams cad de nyid der gcig pas //
NK103(pe)020:1554: ye nas sangs rgyas bde chen nyid //
NK103(pe)020:1555: skye 'gags med pa'i snying po yin //
NK103(pe)020:1556: bya btsal med pa'i dkyil 'khor gsum //

NK103(pe)020:1561: dgongs 'dus kyi khungs drangs pa kye bod pa 'khor
NK103(pe)020:1562: du 'dus pa'i tshogs rgyal ba'i gdung 'tshob pa'i sras
NK103(pe)020:1563: rnams rang gi sems kyi de kho na nyid kyi
NK103(pe)020:1565: dkyil 'khor chen po gsum gyi sgo 'ba' zhig tu
NK103(pe)020:1566: 'jug par bya'o de yang rtsa ba byang chub sems
NK103(pe)020:1567: kyi dal 'ba' zhig gi sgor 'jug par bya'o //

NK103(pe)020:1767: nam mkha' rdo rje'i spyod pa zhes bya la /

NK103(pe)020:1773: kyi rim pa bzhi 'phel ba la sogs pa mang

NK103(pe)020:1775: yi ge mang na rnam par 'khyams par 'gyur bas
NK103(pe)020:1776: spyod pa'o // mi spro'o // mu bzhi kun tu ye rdzogs la //

NK103(pe)020:2107: gong gi bco brgyad de man ngag go //
NK103(pe)020:2108: bcu gnyer yig la sogs pa bsam gtan phran bu
NK103(pe)020:2109: yi ge ris dkyus kyi man ngag shin tu rgyas
NK103(pe)020:2111: snyan brgyud zhal gyi man ngag ni /
NK103(pe)020:2115: grub pa'i chu bo bzhi rdzogs kyi bla ma la rag las shing /
NK103(pe)020:2116: brda bral stong nyid rang sar grol ba'i man ngag ni /
NK103(pe)020:2117: rang gis myong du med pa'i tshul gyis nyams su
NK103(pe)020:2118: myong ba las yi ger brir mi btub pa yin
NK103(pe)020:2119: no // de lta bu'i gsang sngags kyi theg pa'i
NK103(pe)020:2120: tshig don la nges pa ma rnyed pas gzhan la
NK103(pe)020:2122: gang zag gang gis mtshams med pas dmyal bar skye ba'i las /
NK103(pe)020:2123: pha ma dgra bcom gsod pa dang /
NK103(pe)020:2125: de bzhin gshegs pa ngan sems kyis khrag 'byin pa /
NK103(pe)020:2127: chos log par smra ba'i sdig de de bas lci la /
NK103(pe)020:2128: rang don la nges par rtogs pa'i blo shed ma bye bar //
NK103(pe)020:2129: tshig gi lam yi ger don khrid nas ni /
NK103(pe)020:2130: gang la yang blo ma nges par dri ba'i lan brjod na //
NK103(pe)020:2131: sems can srog chags pa kun gyi srog phrogs te bcad pa pas //
NK103(pe)020:2132: rang gis mi shes pa'i chos gzhan la bshad pa de srog bcad pa de bas lci //
NK103(pe)020:2134: rang gis rtogs nas gzhan la smra bar gang byed pa //
NK103(pe)020:2135: de nyid ston pa sangs rgyas nga yin pas dbang lnga yang rdzogs //
NK103(pe)020:2137: slob ma'i ma rig pa'i rab rib sel bar byed pas thur ma dang 'dra ba 'di //
NK103(pe)020:2138: bka' rtags kyi phyag rgya bzhi dang bral ba dang
NK103(pe)020:2139: tshad ma lung rigs man ngag gsum dang 'gal ba'i
NK103(pe)020:2140: skyon // rgyal ba rig 'dzin gang zag dang /
NK103(pe)020:2142: bzod par gsol zhing gnyis su med pa'i ngang du bshags so //
NK103(pe)020:2143: ngal ba'i dge ba 'dis bdag gis rjes su 'brang ba rnams //
NK103(pe)020:2144: shes rab kyi blo mig gi dbang po'i rab rib yongs su dag nas //
NK103(pe)020:2145: theg pa'i blang dor gyi bye brag legs par rtogs shing //
NK103(pe)020:2146: chos nyid mnyam pa nyid kyi don rang rig mngon
NK103(pe)020:2147: sum du mthong ba'i ngang la rgyun du gnas par
NK103(pe)020:2148: smon to // shes rab kyi spyan rnam par 'byed pa zhes bya ba'i man ngag /
